urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msKuS:3.1.14#tadātmaguṇasadbhāvād apratiṣedhaḥ || tasyā ātmaguṇatve sa[ṃ]ti sadbhāvād apratiṣedha ātma[no]〈naḥ〉 yadi smṛtir ātmaguṇaḥ evaṃ sati smṛtir upapadyate nānyadṛṣṭam anyaḥ smaratīti ^" indriyacaitanye tu nānākartṛkāṇāṃ viṣayagrahaṇā〈nā〉2m apratisandhānam apratisandhāne vā viṣayavyavasthānupapattiḥ ekas tu cetano ’nekārthadarśī bhinnanimittaḥ pūrvadṛṣṭam arthaṃ smaratīti ekasyānekārthadarśino darśanapratisandhānāt smṛter ātmaguṇatve sati sadbhāvaḥ viparyaye cānupapattiḥ ^" smṛtyāśra[ya]〈yā〉2prāṇabhṛtāṃ sarve vyavahārāḥ ātmaliṅgam udāharaṇamātram indriyāntaravikāra iti || 16 || aparisaṅkhyānāc ca smṛtiviṣayasya || aparisaṅkhyāya ca smṛtiviṣayam idam ucyate na smṛteḥ smartavyaviṣayatvād iti [pyeṃ]〈ye〉2yaṃ smṛtir agṛhyamāṇe rthe ’jñāsiṣam aham 〈amum〉2 artham iti 〈^"〉2 etasyā jñātṛjñānaviśiṣṭaḥ pūrvajñāto rtho viṣayo nārthamātram jñātavān aham amum artham asau mayā〈rtho〉2 jñātaḥ jñātam asminn arthe mama jñānam abhūd iti caturvidham etad vākyaṃ smṛtiviṣayajñāpakaṃ samānārtham sarvatra khalu jñātā jñānaṃ jñeyaṃ ca gṛhyate atha pratyakṣe rthe yā smṛtis tayā trīṇi jñānāny ekasminn arthe pratisandhīyante samānakartṛkāṇi (KuS 64bv1)na nānākartṛkāṇi nākarttṛkāṇi 〈nākarttṛkāṇi〉2 kiṃ tarhy ekakarttṛkāṇi adrākṣam amum arthaṃ yam evaitarhi paśyāmiṃ adrākṣam iti darśanaṃ darśanasaṃvic ca na khalu saṃvi〈di〉2te [rthe] sve darśane syād etad adrākṣam iti 〈|〉 te khalv ete dve jñāne yam evaitarhi paśyāmīti tṛtīyaṃ jñānam evam eko rthas tribhir jñānair yujyamāno nākartṛko na nānākarttṛko na nānākarttṛkaḥ kiṃ tarhy ekakarttṛka iti 〈^"〉 so yaṃ smṛtiviṣayo ’parisaṅkhyāyamāno vidyamānaḥ prajñāto [rthoḥ]〈rthaḥ〉2 pratiṣidhyate nāsty ātmā smṛteḥ smartavyaviṣayatvād iti [^"^"] na cedaṃ smṛtimātraṃ smartavyamātraviṣayaṃ vā idaṃ khalu jñānapratisandhānavat smṛtipratisandhānam ekasya sarvaviṣayatvāt | eko yaṃ jñātā sarvaviṣayaḥ svāni jñānāni pratisandhatte amum arthaṃ jñāsyāmy amum arthaṃ vijānāmy amum artham ajñāsiṣam amum arthaṃ jijñāsamānaś ciram ajñātvādhyavasyaty ajñāsiṣam iti evaṃ smṛtim api trikālaviśiṣṭāṃ susmūrṣā[ṃ]viśiṣṭāṃ ca pratisandhatte saṃskārasantatimātre tu sattve utpadyotpadya saṃskārās tirobhavanti sa nāsty eko pi saṃskāro yas trikālaviśiṣṭaṃ jñānaṃ smṛtiṃ cānubhavet na cānubhavam antareṇa jñānasya smṛteś ca pratisandhānam ahaṃ mameti cotpadyate dehāntaravat ato numīyate asty ekaḥ sarvaviṣayaḥ pratidehaṃ 〈sva〉2jñā(KuS 65br1)naprabandhaṃ smṛtiprabandhaṃ ca pratisandhatte iti yasya dehāntare[pra]〈ṣu〉2 vṛtter abhāvān na pratisandhānaṃ bhavatīti || 17 ||
urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msKuS:3.1.15#nātmapratipattihetūnāṃ manasi sambhavāt || na [ca] dehādisaṅghātavyatirikta ātmā kasmāt ātmapratipattihetūnāṃ manasi sambhavāt ^" darśanasparśanābhyām ekārthagrahaṇād ity evamādīnām ātmapratipādakānāṃ hetūnāṃ manasi sambhavo yataḥ mano hi sarvaviṣayam iti tasmān na śarīrendriyamanobuddhisaṅghātavyatirikta ātmeti || 18 ||
urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msKuS:3.1.16#jñātur jñānasādhanopapatteḥ saṃjñābhedamātram || jñātuḥ khalu jñānasādhanāny utpadyante cakṣuṣā paśyati ghrāṇena jighrati sparśanena spṛśati evaṃ mantuḥ sarvaviṣayasya matisādhanam antaḥkaraṇabhūtaṃ sarvaviṣayaṃ vidyate yenāyaṃ manyata iti 〈^"〉 evaṃ ca sati jñātary ātmasaṃjñā na mṛṣyate ma[tisādhakaṃ]naḥsaṃjñābhyanujñāyate manasi ca manaḥsaṃjñā na mṛṣyate matisādhanaṃ tv abhyanujñāyate tad idaṃ saṃjñābhedamātraṃ nārthe vivāda iti pratyākhyāne vā sarvendriyavilopaprasaṅgaḥ atha mantuḥ sarvaviṣayasya matisādhanaṃ sarvaviṣayaṃ pratyākhyāyate nāstīti 〈^"〉 evaṃ rūpādiviṣayagrahaṇasādhanāny api na santīti sarvendriyavilopaḥ prasajyata iti || 19 ||
urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msKuS:3.1.17#niyamaś ca niranumānaḥ || yo yaṃ niyama iṣyate rūpādigrahaṇasādhanāny asya (KuS 65bv1)santi matisādhanaṃ sarvaviṣayaṃ nāstīti ^" ayaṃ niranumāno nātrānumānam asti yena niyamaṃ pratipadyāmaha iti rūpādibhyaś ca viṣayā[na]ntaraṃ sukhādayas tadupalabdhau [kā]〈ka〉raṇāntarasadbhāvaḥ 〈^"〉 yathā cakṣuṣā gandho na gṛhyata iti [kā]〈ka〉raṇāntaraṃ ghrāṇam 〈^"〉 evaṃ cakṣurghrāṇābhyāṃ rasoṃ na gṛhyata iti [kā]〈ka〉raṇāntaraṃ rasanaṃ evaṃ śeṣeṣu tathā cakṣurādibhiḥ sukhādayo na gṛhyante iti karaṇāntareṇa bhavitavyam ta[ṃ]c ca jñānāyaugapadyaliṅgam 〈^"〉 yac ca sukhādyupalabdhau karaṇaṃ tac ca jñānāyaugapadyaliṅgam tasyendriyam indriyaṃ prati sannidher asannidher na yugapaj jñānāny utpadyante tatra yad uktam ātmapratipattihetūnāṃ manasi sambhavād iti tad ayuktam 〈||〉
urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msKuS:3.1.18#kiṃ punar ayaṃ dehādisaṅghātād anyo nitya utānitya iti kutaḥ saṃśayaḥ ubhayathā dṛṣṭatvāt saṃśayaḥ ^" vidyamānam ubhayathā bhavati nityam anityaṃ ca pratipādite cātmasadbhāve saṃśayānivṛtter iti ātmasadbhāve hetubhir evāsya prāg dehabhedād avasthānaṃ siddham ūrdhvam api dehabhedād avatiṣṭhate kutaḥ || 19 || pūrvābhyastasmṛtyanubandhāj jātasya harṣabhayaśokasampratipa[ttiḥ]〈tteḥ〉2 || 20 || jātaḥ khalv ayaṃ kumārako smiñ janmany agṛhīteṣu harṣabhayaśokahetuṣu harṣabhayaśokān pratipadyate (KuS 66br1)liṅgānumeyān te ca smṛtyanubandhād utpadyante nānyathā smṛtyanubandhaś ca pūrvābhyāsam antareṇa na bhavati pūrvābhyāsaś ca pūrvajanmani sati nānyathā sidhyaty etat avatiṣṭhate ’yam ūrdhvaṃ śarīrabhedād iti || 20 ||
urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msKuS:3.1.19#padmādiṣu prabodhasaṃmīlanavikāravat tadvikāraḥ || yathā padmādiṣv anityeṣu prabo[dhaḥ]〈dha〉2 saṃmīlanaṃ [ca] vikāro bhavati evam anityasyātmano harṣabhayaśokasampratipattir vikāraḥ syāt hetvabhāvād ayuktam ^" anena hetunā padmādiṣu prabodhasaṃmīlanavikāravad anityasyātmano harṣādisampratipattir iti ^" nātrodāharaṇasādharmyāt sādhyasādhanahetur na vaidharmyād asti hetvabhāvād asambaddhārthakam ucyata iti ^" dṛṣṭāntāc ca ^" harṣādinimittasyānivṛttiḥ yā ceyam āseviteṣu viṣayeṣu harṣādisampratipattiḥ smṛtyanubandhakṛtā pratyātmaṃ gṛhyate seyaṃ padmādisammīlanadṛṣṭāntena na nivartate yathā ceyaṃ na nivartate tathā jātasyāpīti ^" kriyājātaś ca parṇavibhāgaḥ saṃyoga[ḥ]prabodhaḥ saṃmīlane kriyāhetuś cānumeyaḥ ^" evaṃ ca sati kiṃ dṛṣṭāntena pratiṣidhyate ^"^"
urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msKuS:3.1.2#na viṣayavyavasthānāt || na dehādisaṅghātād anyaś cetanaḥ ^" kasmāt viṣayavyavasthānāt vyavasthitaviṣayāṇīndriyāṇi cakṣuṣy asati rūpaṃ na gṛhyate sati ca gṛhyate ^" yac ca tasmi[n sa]〈nn as〉2ati na bhavati sati ca bhavatīti tasya tad iti vijñā[ye]〈ya〉2te ^" tasmād rūpagrahaṇaṃ cakṣuṣaś cakṣū rūpaṃ paśyati evaṃ ghrāṇādiṣv apīti [|| 3 ||] tānīmānīndri[ya]〈yā〉2[‥]〈ṇi〉2 [‥ ‥ ‥ ‥ yo]〈svasva〉2viṣayagrahaṇāc cetanāni [teṣām] [||] indriyāṇāṃ bhāvābhāvayor viṣayagrahaṇasya tathābhāvāt [||] evaṃ sati kim anyena cetanena sandigdhatvād ahetuḥ [||] yo yam indriyāṇāṃ bhāvābhāvayor viṣayagrahaṇasya tathābhāvaḥ sa kim ayaṃ ^" cetana[tvāc]〈tvād〉2 [ce]〈āhosvic ce〉2tanopakaraṇānāṃ [vā] grahaṇanimittatvād iti sandhiyate ^" cetanopakaraṇatve pīndriyāṇāṃ grahaṇanimittatvād bhavitum arhati || 5 ||
