urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msKuS:3.1.26#na saṅkalpanimittatvād rāgādīnām || na khalu saguṇadravyotpattivad utpattir ātmano rāgasya ca ^" kasmāt saṅkalpanimittatvād rāgādīnām ayaṃ khalu prāṇināṃ viṣayān āse[vi]〈va〉2mānānāṃ saṅkalpajanito rāgo gṛhyate saṅkalpaś ca pūrvānubhūtaviṣayānucintanayoniḥ ^" [ye]〈te〉2nānumīyate jātasyāpi pūrvānubhūtārthacintanakṛto rāga iti ^" ātmotpādādhikaraṇāt tu rāgotpattir bhavantī saṅkalpād anyasmin rāgakāraṇe sati vācyā kāryadravyaguṇavat na cātmotpādaḥ siddho nāpi saṅkalpād anyad rāgakāraṇam asti ^" tasmād ayuktaṃ saguṇadravyotpattivat tayor utpattir iti ^" athāpi saṅkalpād anyad rāgakāraṇaṃ dharmādharmalakṣaṇam adṛṣṭam upādīyate tathā(KuS 68r1)pi pūrvaśarīrayogo ’pratyākhyeyaḥ tatra hi tasya nirvṛttiḥ nāsmiñ janmani tanmayatvād rāga iti viṣayābhyāsaḥ khalv ayaṃ bhāvanāhetus tanmayatvam ucyate iti jātiviśeṣāc ca rāgaviśeṣa iti karma khalv idaṃ jātiviśeṣanivarttakaṃ tādarthyā〈ttā〉2cchā[bdaṃ]〈bdyaṃ〉2 vijñāyate tasmād anupapannaṃ saṅkalpād anyad rāgakāraṇam iti
urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msKuS:3.1.27#anādiś cetanasya śarīrayoga ity uktam svakṛtakarmanimittaṃ cāsya śarīraṃ sukhaduḥkhādhiṣṭhānaṃ tat parīkṣyate kiṃ ghrānādivad ekaprakṛtikam uta nānāprakṛtīti kutaḥ saṃśayaḥ vipratipatteḥ saṃśayaḥ pṛthivyādīni bhūtāni saṅkhyāvikalpena śarīraprakṛtir iti pratijānata iti kiṃ tatra tattvam || 27 || pārthivaṃ guṇāntaropalabdheḥ || tatra mānuṣaṃ śarīraṃ pārthivam kasmāt guṇāntaropalabdheḥ gandhavatī pṛthivī gandhavac charīraṃ abādīnām agandhatvāt tatprakṛty agandhaṃ syāt na[nv i]〈 tv i〉2dam abādibhir asaṃpṛktayā pṛthivyārabdhaṃ ceṣṭendriyārthāśrayabhāvena kalpata ity ataḥ pañcānāṃ bhūtānāṃ saṃyoge sati śarīraṃ bhavati bhūtasaṃyogo hi mithaḥ pañcānāṃ na niṣiddha iti āpyataijasavāyavyāni lokāntare śarīrāṇi teṣv api ca bhūtasaṃyogaḥ puruṣārthatantra iti sthālyādidravyaniṣpattāv api niḥsaṃśayo ’nabādisaṃyogam antareṇa niṣpatti(KuS 68v1)r iti ^"
urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msKuS:3.1.28_30#pārthivāpyataijasaṃ tadguṇopalabdheḥ ^" niḥśvāsocchvāsopalabdheś cāturbhautikam 〈^"〉 gandhakledapākavyūhāvakāśadānebhyaḥ pāñcabhautikam ^" ta ime sandigdhāhetava ity upekṣitavān sūtrakāraḥ ^" kathaṃ sandigdhāḥ sati ca prakṛtibhāve bhūtānāṃ dharmopalabdhir asati ca saṃyogāpratiṣedhāt sannihitānām iti ^" yathā sthālyām udakatejovāyvākāśānām iti tad idam anekabhūtaprakṛti śarīram agandham arasam arūpam asparśaṃ ca [vi]〈pra〉2kṛtyanuvidhānāt syāt na tv idam itthambhūtam tasmāt pārthivaṃ guṇāntaropalabdheḥ iti || 28 ||
urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msKuS:3.1.3#yac coktaṃ viṣayavyavasthānā〈d iti〉2 [ta(t)]〈tadā〉2vyavasthānād evā[rtha]〈tma〉2sadbhāvād apratiṣedhaḥ || yadi khalv ekam indriyaṃ vyavasthitaviṣayaṃ sarvajñaṃ sarvaviṣayagrāhi cetanaṃ syāt ^" kas tato 〈’〉2nyaṃ cetanam anumātuṃ śaknuyāt ^" yasmāt tu vyavasthitaviṣayāṇīndriyāṇi tasmāt tebhyo nyaś cetanaḥ sarvajñaḥ sarvaviṣayagrā[hi cetana syāt (KuS 67av1)kas tato nyaṃ cetanam anumātuṃ śaknuyāt yasmāt tu vyavasthitaviṣayāṇīndriyāṇi tasmāt tebhyo nyaś cetanaḥ sarvajñaḥ sarvaviṣayaviṣayagrā]hīviṣayavyava[sthām atī]〈sthi〉2to 〈’〉2numīyate ^" tatredam abhijñānam a[pratyā]〈pyā〉2khyeyam cetanavṛttam udāhriyate rūpadarśī khalv ayaṃ raṃsaṃ gandhaṃ vā pūrvagṛhītam anuminoti ^" gandhapratisaṃvedī ca rūparasāv anuminoti ^" evaṃ viṣayaśeṣe pi [boddhavyam]〈vācyam〉2 rūpaṃ dṛṣṭvā gandhaṃ jighrati gandhaṃ ca ghrātvā rūpaṃ paśyati ^" tad evam aniyataparyāyaṃ sarvaviṣayagrahaṇam ekacetanādhikaraṇam ananyakartṛkaṃ pratisandhatte pratyakṣānumānāgamasaṃśa[yāt]〈ya〉2pratyayāṃś ca nānāviṣayān[ānā]〈svā〉2tmakartṛkān pratisandhāya vedayate sarvārthaviṣayaṃ ca śāstraṃ [pravarttate]〈pratipadyatai〉2 artham aviṣayabhūtaṃ śrotrasya kramabhāvino varṇāñ śrutvā padavākyabhā[vena]〈vaṃ〉2 pratisandhāya śabdārthavyavasthāṃ ca budhyamāno nekaviṣaṃyam arthajā[taṃ]〈ta〉2grahaṇīyam ekaikenendriyeṇa gṛhṇāti ^" seyaṃ sarvajña〈sya〉2 jñeyāvyavasthānānupadaṃ śakyā[ṃ] parikramitum ^" ākṛtimātraṃ tūdāhṛtam ^" tatra yad uktaṃ indriyacaitanye sati kim anyena cetanena tad ayuktaṃ bhavati || 5 ||
urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msKuS:3.1.31#śrutiprāmāṇyāc ca || sūryaṃ te cakṣur gacchatād ity atra mantre pṛthivīṃ te śarīram iti śrūyate tad idaṃ prakṛtau vikārasya pralayābhidhānam iti sūryaṃ te cakṣuḥ spṛṇomīty atra mantrāntare pṛthivīṃ te śarīram iti śrūyate seyaṃ kāraṇād vikārasya spṛtir abhidhīyata iti ^" sthālyādiṣu ca tulyaṃjātīyānām ekakāryārambhadarśanād bhinnajātīyānām ekakāryārambhānupapattiḥ ^"
