urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msKuS:3.1.33#abhautikānīty āha kasmāt || 30 || mahadaṇugrahaṇāt || mahad iti mahattaraṃ mahattamaṃ copalabhyate yathā nyagrodhaparvatādi aṇv ity aṇutaram aṇutamaṃ ca gṛhyate nyagrodhadhānādi tad ubha[yai]〈ya〉m upalabhyamānaṃ cakṣuṣo bhautikatvaṃ bādhate bhautikaṃ hi yāvat tāvad eva vyāpnoti abhautikaṃ tu vibhutvāt sarvavyāpakam iti ^"^"
