urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msL1D:3.1.14#tadātmaguṇasadbhāvād apratiṣedhaḥ | tasyā ātmaguṇatve sati sadbhāvād apratiṣedha ātmanaḥ yadi smṛtir ātmaguṇaḥ evaṃ sati smṛtir upadyate nānyadṛṣṭam anyaḥ smarati | iṃdriyacaitanye [nā]nānākartṛkānāṃ viṣayagrahāṇām apratisaṃdhānaṃ pratisaṃdhāne vā viṣayavyavasthānānupapattiḥ ekas tu cetano ’nekārthadarśīti bhinnanimittaḥ pūrvvadṛṣṭam a[r]vusmaratīti | ekasyānekārthadarśino darśanapratisaṃdhānāt smṛter ātmaguṇatve sati sadbhāvaḥ viparyaye (cā)nupapattiḥ smṛtyāśrayāḥ prāṇabhṛtāṃ sarvve vyavahārāḥ ātmaliṃgam udāharaṇamātram iṃdriyāṃtaravikāra iti | aparisaṃkhyānāc ca smṛtiviṣayasya aparisaṃkhyāya ca smṛtiviṣayam idam ucyate na smṛteḥ smarttavyaviṣayatvād iti | yeyaṃ smṛtir agṛhyamāṇe rthe ajñāsiṣam aham artha iti | eta[sya]〈syā〉 jñātṛjñānaviśiṣṭhaḥ pūrvvajñāto viṣayo nārtha[mo]〈mā〉traṃ jñātavān aham amum arthaṃ asāv artho mayā jñātaḥ asminn arthe bhi[ma] jñānam abhūd iti caturvidham etad vākyaṃ smṛtiviṣayajñāpakaṃ samānārthaṃ sarvvatra khalu jñātā jñānaṃ jñeyaṃ ca gṛhyate | atha pratyakṣe ’rthe yā smṛtis tayā trīṇi jñānāni ekasminn arthe pratisaṃdhīyaṃte samānakartṛkāṇi | na nānākartṛkāṇi kiṃ tarhy ekakartṛkāṇi adrākṣam amum arthaṃ yam evaitarhi paśyāmi | adrākṣam iti darśanaṃ darśanasaṃvic ca | na khalv asaṃvidite sve darśane syād etad adrākṣam iti | te khalv ete dve jñāne yam evaitarhi pa[śya]〈śyā〉mīti tṛtīyam evārthajñānam ekāṃ eko rthas tribhir jñānair abhidyamāno nājñātṛko na nānājñā:kartṛka iti jñeyaṃ smṛtiviṣayo ’parisaṃkhyeyamāno vidyamānaḥ prajñāto rthaḥ pratiṣidhyate nā. ātmā smṛteḥ smarttavyaviṣayatvād iti | na cedaṃ smṛtimātraṃ smṛtimātraṃ smarttavyamātraviṣayaṃ idaṃ khalu jñānapratisaṃdhānavat smṛtipratisaṃ‥(na)m ekasya sarvvaviṣayatvāt | eko yaṃ jñātā sarvvaviṣayaḥ svāni jñānāni pratisaṃ[dhā]〈dha〉tte | amum arthaṃ jñāsyāmi jānāmi ajñāsiṣam amum arthaṃ jijñāsamānaś ciram ajñātvādhyavasyaty ajñāsiṣam iti | evaṃ smṛtim api trikālaviśiṣṭāṃ susmūrṣāviśiṣṭāṃ ca pratisaṃdhatte | saṃskārasaṃtatimātre tu satve utpadyotpadya saṃskārās tirobhava[ṃ]ti | sa nāsty eko pi saṃskāro yas trikālaviśiṣṭajñānaṃ smṛtiṃ cānubhavet | na cānubhavam aṃtareṇa jñānasya smṛteś ca pratisaṃdhānam ahaṃ mameti cotpadyate dehāṃtaravat | ato numīyate | asty ekaḥ sarvvaviṣayaḥ pratidehaṃ svājñānapravaṃdhaṃ smṛtiprativaṃdhaṃ ca pratisaṃdhatta iti | yasya dehāṃtareṣu vṛtter abhāvāt pratisaṃdhānan na bhavatīti |
