urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msL1D:3.1.16#jñātur jñānasādhanopapatteḥ saṃjñābhedamātraṃ | jñātuḥ khalu jñānasādhanāny upapadyaṃtte | cakṣuṣā paśyati ghrāṇena jighrati sparśanena spṛśati | evaṃ maṃtuḥ sarvvaviṣayam itisādhanam aṃtaḥkaraṇabhūtaṃ sarvvaviṣayaṃ vidyate yenāyaṃ manyata iti | evaṃ sati jñātaryy ātmasaṃjñā na mṛṣyate | manasi ca manaḥsaṃjñā na mṛṣyate | matisādhanasaṃjñā mṛṣyate matisādhanam abhyanujñāyate | tad idaṃ saṃjñābhedamātraṃ nātma〈ni〉 vivāda iti | pratyākhyāne vā sarvveṃdriyavilopaprasaṃgaḥ atha maṃtuḥ sarvvaviṣayasya matisādhanaṃ sarvvaviṣayaṃ pratyākhyāyate nāstīti | evaṃ rūpādiviṣayagrahaṇasādhanāny api na bhavaṃti iti sarvveṃdriyaviṣayalopaḥ prasajyata iti |
urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msL1D:3.1.17#niyamaś ca niranumānaḥ | yo yaṃ niyama iṣyate rūpādigrahaṇasādhanāny asya saṃti | matisādhanaṃ sarvvaviṣayaṃ nāstīti ayaṃ niranumāno nānumānam asti yena niyamaṃ pratipadyāmaha iti rūpādibhyaś ca viṣayāṃ[ti]〈ta〉raṃ sukhādayas tadupalabdhau karaṇāṃtarasadbhāvaḥ yathā cakṣuṣā gaṃdho na gṛhyata iti karaṇāṃtaraṃ ghrāṇam evaṃ cakṣurghrāṇābhyāṃ raso na gṛhyate iti karaṇāṃtaraṃ rasanaṃ | evaṃ śeṣeṣv api | tathā cakṣurādibhiḥ sukhādayo na gṛhyaṃta iti kāraṇāṃtareṇa bhavitavyaṃ tac ca jñānayaugapadya[ṃ]liṃgaṃ | yac ca sukhādyupalabdhau karaṇaṃ tac ca jñānāyaugapadyaliṃgaṃ tasyeṃdriyam iṃdriyaṃ prati sannidher asaṃnnidheḥ na yugapat jñānāny utpadyaṃta iti | yatra tad uktam ātmapratipattihetūnāṃ manasi saṃbhavād iti tad ayuktaṃ
urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msL1D:3.1.18#kiṃ punar ayaṃ dehādisaṃghātād anyo nitya utānitya iti | kutaḥ saṃśayaḥ ubhayathā dṛṣṭatvāt saṃśayaḥ vidyamānam ubhayathā bhavati | nityam anityaṃ ca pratipādite cātmasabhaṃve saṃśayānivṛtter iti | ātmasadbhāvahetubhir evāsya prāg dehabhedād avasthānaṃ siddhaṃ | ūrdhvam api dehabhedād avatiṣṭhate | kutaḥ pūrvvābhyastasmṛtyanuvaṃdhāj jātasya harṣabhayaśokasaṃpratipatteḥ 〈|〉 jātaḥ khalv ayaṃ kumārako asmin janmani agṛhīteṣu harṣabhayaśokahetuṣu harṣabhayaśokān pratipadyate liṃgānumeyān | te ca smṛtyanuvaṃdhād utpadya[‥]〈nte〉 nānyathā | smṛtyanuvaṃdhaś ca pūrvvābhyāsam aṃtareṇa na bhavati | pūrvvābhyāsaś ca pūrvvajanmani sati nānyathoti sidhyaty etad avatiṣṭhate | ayam ūrddhvaṃ śarīrabhedād iti |
urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msL1D:3.1.19#padmādiṣu pravodhasammīlanavikāravat tadvikāraḥ 〈|〉 yathānityeṣu padmādiṣu pravodhas sammīlanaṃ vikāro bhavati | evam anityātmano harṣabhayaśokasaṃpratipattiḥ syāt | hetvabhāvād ayuktaṃ anena hetunā padmādiṣu pravodhasammīlanavikāravad anityasyātmano harṣādisaṃpratipāttir iti | nātrodāharaṇasā[ṣa]rmyāt sādhyasādhanaṃ hetur na vaidharmyād asti hitvabhāvāt | asaṃvaddhārthakam apārthakam ucya[ite]〈te i〉ti | dṛṣṭāṃtāc ca harṣādinimittasyānivṛttiḥ | yā ceyam āseviteṣu viṣayeṣu harṣādisaṃpratipattiḥ smṛtyanuvaṃdhakṛtā pratyātmaṃ gṛhyate seyaṃ padmādisammīlanadṛṣṭāntena na nivarttyate | yathā ceyaṃ na nivarttyate tathā jātasyāpīti kriyājātaś ca parṇasaṃyogavibhāgāḥ pravodhasammīlane kriyā(h)etuś ca kriyānumeyaḥ | evaṃ ca kiṃ dṛṣṭāntena pratiṣidhyate |
