urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msL1D:3.1.24#itaś ca nitya ātmā kasmāt vītarāgajanmādarśanāt | sarāgo jāyata ity arthād āpadyate | ayaṃ jāya〈māna〉 ity arthād āpadyate | ayaṃ jāyamāno rāgānuvaddho jāyate | rāgasya ca pūrvvānubhūtaviṣayānuciṃtanaṃ yoniḥ pūrvvānubhavaś ca viṣayāṇāṃ pūrvvasmin na janma[ṃ]ni śarīram aṃtareṇotpadyate so yam ātmā pūrvvaśarīrānubhūtān viṣayān anusmaran teṣu teṣu rajyate tathā cāyaṃ dvayoḥ pratisaṃdhiḥ evaṃ pūrvvaśarīrasya pūrvatareṇa pūrvatarasya pūrvvatamenetyādinā’nādiḥ cetanasya śarīrayogaḥ anādiś ca rāgānuvaṃdha iti siddhaṃ nityatvam iti |
