urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msL1D:3.1.26#na saṃkalpanimittatvād rāgādīnāṃ | na kha[lva]〈lu〉 saguṇadravyotpattivat tadutpattir ātmano rāgasya ca kasmāt saṃkalpani〈mi〉ttatvād rāgādīnāṃ | ayaṃ khalu prāṇināṃ viṣayān āsevamānānāṃ saṃkalpajanito rāgo gṛhyate | saṃkalpaś ca pūrvvānubhūtaviṣayānuciṃtanayoniḥ tenānumīyate jātasyāpi pūrvvānubhūtārthaciṃtanakṛto rāga iti | ātmotpādādhikaraṇānāṃ tu rāgotpattir bhavatīti saṃkalpād anyasmin rāgakaraṇe sati vācyā kāryadravyaguṇavat | na cātmotpādaḥ siddho nāpi saṃkalpād anyad rāgakāraṇam asti |tasmād ayuktaṃ saguṇadravyotpattivat tayor utpattiḥ | athāpi saṃkalpād anyad rāgakaraṇaṃ dharmādharmalakṣaṇam adṛṣṭam upādīyate | tathāpi pūrvvaśarīrayogo ’pratyākhyeyaḥ tatra hi tasya nirvṛttiḥ nāsmin janmani tanmayatvād rāga iti | viṣayābhyāsaḥ khalv ayaṃ bhāvanāhetuḥ tanmayatvam ucyata iti | jātiviśeṣāc ca rāgaviśeṣa iti | karma khalv idaṃ jātiviśeṣanivarttakaṃ tādārthyātmyāt tācha[dyaṃ]〈bdyaṃ〉 vijñāyate tasmāt tad anupapannaṃ saṃkalpād anyad rāgakāraṇam iti |
urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msL1D:3.1.27#anādiś cetanasya śarīrayoga ity uktaṃ svakṛtakarmanimittaṃ cāsya śarīre sukhaduḥ[kha]〈khā〉dhiṣṭhānaṃ tat parīkṣyate | kiṃ ghrānādivad ekaprakṛtikaṃ uta nānāprakṛtīti kutaḥ saṃśayaḥ vipratipatteś ca saṃśayaḥ pṛthivyādīni bhūtāni saṃkhyāvikalpena śarīraprakṛtir iti pratijānīta iti kiṃ tatra tatvaṃ | pārthivaṃ guṇāṃtaropala(bdhe) tatra mānuṣaṃ śarīraṃ pārthivaṃ kasmāt guṇāṃtaropalabdheḥ gaṃdhavatī pṛthivī gaṃdhavac ca śarīraṃ avādīnām agaṃdhavatvāc ca tatprakṛty agaṃdhaṃ syāt na tv idam avādibhir asaṃpṛktayā pṛthivyārabdha ceṣṭeṃdriyāśrayabhāvena kalpata itaḥ paṃcānāṃ bhūtānāṃ saṃyoge sati śarīraṃ bha〈va〉2ti bhūtasaṃyogo mithaḥ paṃcānāṃ na niṣiddha iti | āpyataijasavāyavyāni lokāṃtare śarīrāṇi teṣv api bhūtasaṃyogaḥ puruṣārthataṃtra iti | sthālyādidravyaniḥpattāv api niḥsaṃśayā nāvādisaṃyogam aṃtareṇa niṣpattir iti |
urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msL1D:3.1.28_30#pārthivāpyataijasa tadguṇopalabdheḥ | niḥśvāsocchvāsopalabdheś cāturbhautikaṃ | gaṃdhakledapākavyūhāvakāśadānebhyaḥ pāṃcabhautikaṃ itīme saṃdigdhā’hetava ity upekṣitavān sūtrakāraḥ kathaṃ saṃdigdhā iti | sati prakṛtibhāve bhūtānāṃ dharmopalabdhir asati ca saṃyogāpratiṣedhāt sannihitānām iti yathā sthālyām udakatejovāyvākāśānām iti | tad ida[m e]〈m a〉anekabhūtaprakṛti śarīram agaṃdham arasam arūpam asparśaṃ ca prakṛtyanuvidhānāt syāt na tv idam itthaṃbhūtaṃ tasmāt pārthivaṃ guṇāṃtaropalabdheḥ
