urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msL1D:3.1.6#na kāryāśrayakartṛvadhāt 〈|〉 na vrūmo nityasya satvasya ca rśo hiṃsā api tv anuchittidharmakasya satvasya kāryāśrayasya śarīrasya svaviṣayopalabdhe〈ḥ〉 kartṝṇām iṃdriyāṇām upaghātaḥ pīḍā vaikalyalakṣaṇaḥ pravaṃdhochedo vā | pramāpaṇālakṣaṇo vā vadho hiṃseti kāryaṃ tu sukhaduḥkhasaṃvedanaṃ tasyādhiṣṭhānam āśrayaṃ śarīraṃ | kāryāśrayasya śarīrasya svaviṣayopalabdheś ca kartṝṇām iṃdriyāṇāṃ vadho hiṃsā na nityasyātmanaḥ | tatra yad uktaṃ sātmakapradāho pi tannityatvād ity etad ayuktaṃ yasya satvochedo hiṃsā tasya kṛtahānam akṛtābhyāgamaś ceti doṣaḥ | etāvac ca tat syāt | satvochedo hiṃsānuchittidharmakasya vā satvasya kāryasyāśrayakartṛvādhaḥ na kalpāṃtaram anyad asti | satvochedaś ca pratiṣiddhaḥ tatra kim anya cheṣaṃ yathābhūtam iti athavā kāryāśrayasya kartṛvadhād iti kāryāśrayasya kartṛvadhād iti | kāryāśrayo deheṃdriyavuddhisaṃghāto nityasyātmanaḥ tatra sukhaduḥkhapratisaṃvedanaṃ tasyāyiṣṭhānamātrāśrayaḥ tadāyatanaṃ tad bhavati na tato nya(tre)ti sa eva karttā tannimittā sukhaduḥkhasaṃvedanasya nirvṛttiḥ na tam aṃtareṇeti tasya vādha upaghātaḥ pīḍā pramāpaṇaṃ vā hiṃsā na nityatvenātmochedaḥ tatra yad uktaṃ tada[‥]〈..〉vaḥ sātmakapradāhe pi tannityatvād etan neti |
