urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msM2D:3.1.11#dṛṣṭāṃtavirodhād apratiṣedhaḥ | [.. ..]〈kara〉ṇadravya vibhāge kāryadravyam avatiṣṭate nityatvaprasaṃgāt kathaṃ tarhy upapadyate yadi kāraṇavibhāgānnīva tiṣṭate bahuṣu tv avayaviṣu yasya kāraṇavibhāgaḥ tasya vināśo yeṣāṃ kāraṇāny avibhaktāni tāny evāvatiṣṭaṃte [buddhiṣu tv avayaviṣu] iti | athavā dṛśyamānārthavirodho dṛṣṭāṃtavirodhaḥ mṛtasya hi kapāle dvāv acaṭau nāsāsthivyavahi(tau) cakṣuṣoḥ sthāna(ṃ) bhedena gṛhyete | na caitad dekasmin nāsāsthivyavahite saṃbhavatīti | athavā ekavināśasyāniyamā dvāv imāv arthau tau ca pṛthag āvaraṇopaghātau ato ’vasīyate dvāv iti | avapīḍanāc caikasya cakṣuṣo raśmiviṣayasaṃnikarṣasya bhedād dṛśyabheda iva gṛhyate | etac ca ekatve virudhyate | atra pīḍananivṛttau dvābhinnapratisaṃdhānam ivagṛhyate | tasmād ekasya vyavadhānānupapattir iti |
