urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msM2D:3.1.14#yadi smṛtir ātmaguṇa evam asti smṛtir ity upapadyate | nānya[ddṛ]〈dṛ〉ṣṭam anyaḥ smaratīti iṃdriyacaitanye tu nānākartṛkāṇāṃ viṣayagrahaṇānām apratisaṃdhānaṃ pratisaṃdhāne vā viṣayavyavasthānānupapattiḥ | ekas tu cetano ’nekārthadarśī nimittatve darśanena pūrvadṛṣṭam arthaṃ smaratīti ekasyānekārthadarśi[noḥ]〈naḥ〉 | tadātmaguṇasadbhāvād apratiṣedhaḥ | dharmo guṇabhūtaḥ smṛtir iti | smṛter ātmaguṇatve[na] sati sadbhāvaḥ | viparyaye ca sati sadbhāvānupapattir iti |smṛtyāśrayāś ca sarbe prāṇabhṛṭāṃ vyavahārāḥ | ātmaliṅgam udāharaṇamātram iṃdriyāṃtaravikāra iti | aparisaṃkhyānāc ca smṛtiviṣayasya | aparisaṃkhyāya ca smṛtiviṣaya ucyate | na smṛteḥ smarttavyaviṣayatvād iti yeyaṃ smṛtir agṛhyamāṇārthe a〈ji〉jñāsiṣam aham amum artham iti | asyā tṛnmānaviśiṣṭaḥ pūrbajñāto ’rtho viṣayo nārthamātraṃ jñātavān aham amum arthaṃ asāv artho jñātaḥ | amusminn arthe jñānam abhūd iti | caturvidham apy etad vākyaṃ smṛtiviṣayajñāpakaṃ samānārthaṃ sarbatra khalv atra jñātā jñānaṃ jñeyaṃ ca gṛhyate | atha pratyakṣe rthe yā smṛtiḥ tatra trīṇi jñānāny ekārthe pratisaṃdhīyaṃte | samānanyāyakāṇi adrākṣam aham amum arthaṃ yam eva tarhi paśyāmīti adrākṣam iti draśanaṃ darśanasaṃvic ca na khlav asaṃvidite sva darśane syād etad adrākṣam iti te khalv ete dve jñāne yam etarhi paśyāmīti tṛtīyam eko rthas tribhir jñānair vudhyamāno rājñātṛko na nanottkātṛkaḥ so yaṃ smṛtiviṣaye parisaṃkhyāyamāne vidyamānaḥ prajñāto ’rthaḥ pratiṣidhyatenāsty ātmā smṛteḥ smarttavyaviṣayaḥ syād iti | na cedaṃ smṛtimātraṃ smarttavyārthamātraviṣayaṃ | idaṃ khalu [..]〈(yā)〉vat smṛtisaṃdhānam ekasya sarvaviṣayatvāt | eko yaṃ jñātā sarbaviṣayaḥ svāni jñānāni pratisaṃdhatte | amum arthaṃ vijñāsyāmīti vijānāmi vyajñāsiṣam amum arthaṃ jijñāsamānaś ciram ajñātvāvyavajñāsiṣam iti | evaṃ smṛtim api svaṃ[mū]〈mu〉rṣāviśiṣṭāṃ trikālaviśiṣṭāṃ ca pratisaṃdhatte saṃdhāvasatam iti | mā tre satve [..]〈nu〉tpadyotpadya saṃskārās tirobhavaṃti | nāsty ekaḥ saṃskāryyaḥ trikālaviśiṣṭaṃ jñānaṃ smṛtiṃ vā anubhaven na bhāvam anubhāvam aṃtareṇa jñānasya smṛteś ca pratisaṃdhānam ahaṃ mameti copapadyate dehāṃtaravad ato ’numīyate | sty ekaḥ sarvaviṣaye yaḥ pratidehaṃ sa[ṃ]jñānaprabaṃdhaṃ smṛtiprabaṃdhaṃ ca pratisandhatta iti yasmād [ve]〈de〉hāṃtareṣu vṛtter abhāvāt pratisaṃdhānaṃ bhavatīti |
urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msM2D:3.1.15#nātmapratipattihetūnāṃ manasi saṃbhavāt | na dehādisaṃghātavyatirikta ātmā | kasmād ātmapratipattihetūnāṃ manasi saṃbhavāt | darśanasparśanābhyām ekārthagrahaṇād ity evamādīnām ātmaprativedanāhetūnāṃ manasi saṃbhavaḥ mano hi sarvaviṣayam iti | tasmād deheṃdriyamanobuddhisaṃghātān na vyatirikta ātmeti |
