urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msM2D:3.1.26#na saṃkalpanimittatvād rāgādīnāṃ | na khalu saguṇadravyotpattivat tayor utpattir ātmano rāgasya ca | kasmāt saṃkalpanimittatvād rāgādīnām ayaṃ khalu prāṇināṃ viṣayāṇām evamānānāṃ saṃkalpajanito rāgo gṛhyate | saṃkalpaś ca pūrbānubhūtaviṣayānuciṃtanaṃ tenānumīyate | jātasyāpi rāgāt | pūrvānubhūtaviṣayaciṃtanakṛta iti | ātmotpādādhikaraṇā ca rāgotpattir bhavatīti saṃkalpād anyasmin rāgakāraṇe sati vācyā kāryyadravyaguṇavan naḥ tadutpādaḥ siddho nāpi saṃkalpād anyad rāgakāraṇam asti | tasmād ayuktaṃ | saguṇadravyotpattivat tadutpattir iti | athāpy anyad rāgakāraṇaṃ dharmalakṣaṇam adṛṣṭaṃ karmābhyādadīta tathāpi pūrbaśarīrayoge pratyākhyeyaṃ | tatra hi tasmiṃs tasya nirvatir [mā]〈nā〉smin janmanīti | tanmayatvād rāgaḥ jātiviśeṣaś ca rāga[ṃ]viśeṣaḥ | tasmād anupapannaṃ saṃkalpād anyad rāgakāraṇam iti |
