urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msM2D:3.1.4#itaś ca vyatirikta ātmā na dehādisaṃghātamātraṃ | śarīradāhe pātakābhāvāt | śarīreṃdriyabuddhivedanāsaṃghātaḥ prā[rṇa]〈ṇī〉bhūto gṛhyate | prāṇibhūta caśarīraṃ [ha]〈da〉dahataḥ prāṇihiṃsākṛtaṃ pāpaṃ pātakaṃ nety ucyate | tasyābhāve tatphalena karttur asaṃghātā[t] | akarttuś ca saṃbadhāt | śarīreṃdriyabuddhivedanāprabaṃdhe khalv anyaḥ saṃghāta utpadyate akṣāṇi rudhyaṃte utpādanirodhasaṃtatibhūtāś ca prabaṃdhā nānyatvaṃ bādhaṃtedehādeḥ saṃghāte syānānyatvādhiṣṭānatvāt | anyatvādhiṣṭāno hy asau prakhyāyata iti | evaṃ ca sati yo dehādisaṃghātaḥprāṇibhūto hiṃsāṃ karoti | nāsau hiṃsāphalena saṃbadhyate | niścayaṃ badhyate | na hiṃsā kṛtād evaṃ satvabhede kṛtahānam akṛtābhyāgamaś ca prasajyate || sati ca satvabhede satvanirodhe vākarmanimittaḥ satvasargaṃ prāpnoti | sa tatra muktyartho vayavaryavāso nopapadyate | tad yadi saṃghātamātraṃ satvaṃ syāt śarīradāhe (vā)takaṃ na bhaved dagdhuś ca [bhe]〈bha〉ved aniṣṭaṃ caitat tasmāt saṃghātavyatirikta ātmā nitya iti |
