urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msM2D:3.1.6#na kāryyāśrayakartṛbadhāt | na brūmo nityasya satvasya vadhāt hiṃseti | kiṃ tarhi anucittidharmakasya satvasya kāryyāśrayasya ca śarīrasya svaviṣayopalabdheś ca kartṝṇāṃm iṃdriyāṇām upaghātaḥ pīḍā vaikalyyalakṣaṇaḥ prabaṃdhochedo vā pramāṇalakṣaṇo baṃdho hiṃseti | kāryyaṃ tu sukhaduḥkhapratisaṃvedanaṃ tasyāyatanam adhiṣṭhānam āśrayaḥ śarīraṃ kā[ryyāṃ]〈ryyā〉śrayasya ca viṣayopalabdheś ca kartṝṇām ceṃdriyāṇāṃ vadho hiṃsā na nityasyātmanaḥ | tatra yad uktaṃ tadabhāvaḥ sātmakapradāhe pi tannityatvād ity etad ayuktam iti | yasya tu satvochedo hiṃsā tasya kṛtahānam akṛtābhyāgamaś ca doṣa etāvac caitat syāt satvochedo vā hiṃsā anucchittidharmakasya vā satvasya vā sa[ṃ] ca kāryyāśrayakartṛvadho na kalpāṃtaram asti | satvochedasya pratiṣiddhaḥ tatra kim anya cheṣaṃ | yathābhūtam iti | athavā kāryāśrayakartṛbadhād iti deheṃdriyabuddhisaṃghāto nityasyātma[ni]〈ne〉 nityasyātmano yat sukhaduḥkhapratisaṃvedanaṃ tasyāśrayas tadā[śri]〈śra〉yinaṃ tad bhava ti na tato ’nyatreti | sa eva karttā tannimittā sukhaduḥkhavedanāsya ni[rvṛ]〈vṛ〉ttir na tadaṃtareṇeti | tasya vadha upaghātaḥ pīḍā pramāpaṇaṃ vā | hiṃ[śa]〈sā〉 nitya[..]〈tve〉na nātmochedasya tatra yad uktaṃ | tadabhāvaḥ sātmakapradāhe pi tannityatvād ity etad ayuktaṃ |
urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msM2D:3.1.7#itaś ca dehādivyatirikta ātmā | savyadṛṣṭasyetareṇa praty[ā]〈a〉bhijñānāt pū[rṣā]〈rvā〉parayor jñānayoḥ pratisaṃdhijñānaṃ pratyabhijñānaṃ yam aham adrākṣaṃ tam eva tarhi jānāmi | yad vā saiṣa sa evāyam artha iti | savyena khalu cakṣuṣā dṛṣṭam artham itareṇāpi cakṣuṣā dṛṣṭāpratyabhijānāti yam aham a[drī]〈drā〉kṣaṃ tam evaṃ vai tarhi paśyāmīti | iṃdriye caitanye ca nānyadṛṣṭam anyaḥ pratyabhijānātīti pratyabhijñānānupapattir asti tv idaṃ pratyabhijñānaṃ tasmād iṃdriyavyatiriktaś cetana iti |
