urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msMy2D:3.1.11#dṛṣṭāṃtavirodhād apratiṣedhaḥ || na kāraṇadravya-vibhāge kāryadravyam avatiṣṭhate nityatvaprasaṃgāt | bahuṣv avayaviṣu yasya kāraṇā〈ni〉 vi[bhā]〈bha〉[(va)sta]〈ktāni ta〉sya vināśaḥ yeṣāṃ kāraṇāny avibhaktāni te tv avatiṣṭhaṃte | athavā dṛśyamānārthavirodho dṛṣṭāṃtavirodhaḥ mṛtasya hi śiraḥkapāle dvāv avaṭau nāsāsthi[(tyai)]vyavahitau cakṣu[ṣāḥ](ṣaḥ) sthāne gṛhyete na caitad ekasmin nā〈sā〉sthivyavahite saṃbhavatīti | athavā eṃkavināśasyāniyamāt | dvāv imāv arthau tau ca pṛthag āvaraṇopaghātāv anumīyete vibhinnāv iti | avapīḍanāc caikasya cakṣuṣo raśmiviṣayasaṃnnikarṣabhedād dṛśyabheda iva gṛhyate ta[ccai]c caikatve virudhyate avapīḍananivṛttau cābhinnaṃ pratisaṃdhānam iti | tasmād ekasya vyavadhānānupapattiḥ |
urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msMy2D:3.1.12#anumīyate cāyaṃ dehādisaṃghātavyatiriktaś cetanaḥ || iṃdriyāṃtaravikārāt || kasyacid amlaphalasya rasena gṛhītasāhacarye rūpe gaṃdhe vā kenacid iṃdriyāṃtareṇa gṛhyamāṇe rasanasyeṃdriyāṃtarasya vikāro rasānusmṛtau rasagardhipravarttito daṃtodakasaṃplavabhūto gṛhyate tasyeṃdriyacaitanye nupapattiḥ | nānyadṛṣṭam anyaḥ smaratīti ||
urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msMy2D:3.1.13#na smṛteḥ smartavyaviṣayatvāt || smṛtir nāma dharmo nimittād utpadyate tasyāḥ smartavyo viṣayaḥ tatkṛta iṃdriyāṃtaravikāro nātmakṛta iti ||
urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msMy2D:3.1.14#tadātmaguṇasadbhāvād apratiṣedhaḥ || tasyā ātmaguṇatve sati sadbhāvād apratiṣedha ātmanaḥ yadi smṛtir ātmaguṇa evaṃ sati smṛtir u[tpa]〈papa〉padyate nānyadṛṣṭam anyaḥ smaratīti | iṃdriyacaitanye nānākartṛkāṇāṃ viṣayagrahaṇānām apratisaṃdhānaṃ pratisaṃ[dho]〈dhā〉ne vā viṣayavyavasthānupapattiḥ || ekas tu cetano anekārthadarśī bhinnanimittaḥ pūrvadṛṣṭam ar(tha)ṃ smaratīty ekasyānekārthadarśino darśanapratisaṃdhānāt smṛter ātmaguṇatve sati sadbhāvo viparyaye ca sadbhāvānupapatti[|]r iti smṛtyāśrayāś ca prāṇabhṛtāṃ vyavahārā ātmaliṃgam udāharaṇamātra[ṃ]m iṃdriyāṃtaravikāra iti | aparisaṃkhyānāc ca smṛtiviṣayasya | aparisaṃkhyāya ca smṛtiviṣayam idam ucyate na smṛteḥ[r] smartavyaviṣayatvād iti | yeyaṃ smṛtir agṛhyamāṇe ’rthe ’jñāsiṣam aham amum artham iti etasyā jñātṛjñānaviśiṣṭaḥ pūrvajñāto rtho viṣayo nārthamātraṃ jñātavān aham amum artham asāv arthoṃ mayā jñāto muṣminn arthe 〈mama〉 jñānam abhūd iti caturvidham apy etad vākyaṃ smṛtiviṣayajñāpakaṃ samānārthaṃ sarvatra khalu jñātā jñānaṃ jñeyaṃ ca gṛhyate | atha pratyakṣe ’rthe yā smṛtis tayā trīṇi jñānāny ekasminn arthe pratisaṃdhīyaṃte samānakartṛkāṇi 〈na〉 nānākartṛkāṇi nākartṛkāṇi kiṃ tarhy ekakartṛkāṇi adrākṣam im arthaṃ yam etarhi paśyāmīti adrākṣam iti darśanaṃ darśanasaṃvic ca na khalv asaṃvidite sve darśane syād etad adrākṣam iti [|] te khalv ete 〈dve〉 jñāne yam evaitarhi paśyāmīti tṛtīyaṃ jñānaṃ | evam eko rthas tribhi jñānair yujyamāno nākartṛko na nānākartṛkaḥ kiṃ tarhy ekakartṛkaḥ so yaṃ smṛtiviṣarye parisaṃkhyā〈ya〉māno vidyamānaḥ prajñāto rthaḥ pratiṣidhyate nāsty ātmā smṛteḥ smartavyaviṣayatvād iti | na cedaṃ smṛtimātraṃ smartta[.]vyārthamātraviṣayaṃ ^" iṃdaṃ khalu jñānapratisaṃdhānavat smṛtipratisaṃdhānam ekasya sarvaviṣayatvāt ^" eko yaṃ jñātā sarvaviṣayaḥ svāni jñānāni pratisaṃdhatte amuṃm arthaṃ jñāsyāmi amum arthaṃ vijānāmy amum arthaṃ vyajñāsiṣam amum arthaṃ jijñāsamānaś ciram ajñātvāvyajñā-siṣam iti | evaṃ smṛtim api trikālaviśiṣṭāṃ susmūrṣāviśiṣṭāṃ ca pratisaṃdhatta iti | saṃskārasaṃtatimātre tu [sva] satve utpadyotpadya saṃskārās tirobhavaṃti | sa nāsty eko pi saṃskāro yas trikālaviśiṣṭaṃ jñānaṃ smṛtiṃ vānubhavet | na cānubhavam aṃtareṇa jñānasya smṛteś ca pratisaṃdhānaṃ 〈ahaṃ〉 mameti cotpadyate dehāṃtarava〈t ta〉to 〈anumīyate〉 sty ekaḥ [.] sarvaviṣayo yaḥ pratidehaṃ svajñānapraba[‥]〈dhaṃ〉 smṛtiprabaṃdhaṃ ca pratisaṃdhatta iti yasya dehāṃtareṣu vṛtter abhāvāt pratisaṃdhānaṃ na bhavatīti || ||
urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msMy2D:3.1.15#nātmapratipattihetūnāṃ manasi saṃbhavāt || na dehādisaṃghātavyatirikta ātmā ^" kasmāt ātmapratipattihetūnāṃ manasi saṃbha[vā]vāt | darśanasparśanābhyām ekārthasya grahaṇād ity evamādīnām ātmapratipattihetūnāṃ manasi saṃbhavo yataḥ mano hi sarvaviṣyam iti | tasmād deheṃdriyamanobuddhisaṃghātān na vyatirikta ātmeti ||
