urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msMy2D:3.1.17#niyamaś ca niranumānaḥ | yo yaṃ niyama iṣyate [p.]rūpādigrahaṇasādhanāny asya matisādhanaṃ sarvaviṣayaṃ nāstīti ayaṃ niranumāno nātrānumānam asti yena niyamaṃ pratipadyemahīti | rūpādibhyaś ca viṣayāṃtaraṃ sukhādayas tadupalabdhau karaṇāṃtarasadbhāvaḥ | yathā cakṣuṣā gaṃdho na gṛhyata iti karaṇāṃtaraṃ ghrāṇaṃ evaṃ cakṣurghrāṇābhyāṃ raso na gṛhyata iti karaṇāṃtaraṃ rasanaṃ evaṃ śeṣeṣu tathā cakṣurādibhiḥ sukhādayo na gṛhyaṃta iti karaṇāṃtareṇa bhavitavyaṃ[m iti] | tac ca jñānāyaugapadyaliṃgaṃ yac ca tat sukhādyupalabdhau karaṇāṃtara jñānāyaugapadyaliṃgaṃ tasya hīṃdriyam iṃdriyaṃ prati sannidher asannidheś ca na yugapat jñānāny utpadyaṃta iti | tatra yad uktam ātmapratipattihetūnāṃ manasi saṃbhavād it[ty]〈ti〉 tad ayuktaṃ || ||
