urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msMy2D:3.1.6#na kāryāśrayakartṛvadhāt || na brūmo nityasya satvasya vadho hiṃseti kiṃ tarhi anuchittidharmakasya satvasya kāryāśrayasya śarīrasya svaviṣayopalabdheś ca kartṝṇām iṃdriyāṇām upaghātaḥ pīḍā vaikalyalakṣaṇaḥ prabaṃdhochedo vā pramāpaṇalakṣaṇo vā vadho hiṃsā ^" kāryaṃ tu sukhaduḥkhapratisaṃvedanaṃ tasyāyatanam adhiṣṭhānam āśrayaḥ (vṛṃ) śarīraṃ kāryāśrayasya 〈śarīrasya〉 svaviṣayopalabdheś ca kartṝṇām iṃdriyāṇāṃ vadho hiṃsā na nityasyātmanaḥ tatra yad uktaṃ tadabhāvaḥ sātmaka[(se)]pradāhe pi tanvityatvād ity eta〈d a〉yuktam iti | yasya tu satvochedo hiṃsā tasya kṛtahānam akṛtābhyāgamaś ceti doṣaḥ | etāvac caitat syāt | satvochedo vā hiṃsā anuchittidharmaka[sya]sya satvasya kāryāśrayakartṛvadho vā hiṃsā na kalpāṃtaram asti satvochedaś ca prati[(si)]〈ṣi〉ddhaḥ [|] tatra kim anya cheśaṃ yathābhūtam iti | atha[|]vā kāṃryāśrayakartṛvadhād iti 〈kāryāśrayo〉 deheṃdriyabuddhisaṃghāto nityasyātmano yat [|] sukhaduḥkhapratisaṃ[dhā]〈veda〉naṃ tasyāśrayas tadāyatanaṃ tad bhavati na tato nya[d i]〈tre〉ti sa eva karttā tannimittā hi sukhaduḥkhasaṃvedanasya nirvṛttir na tadaṃtareṇeti | tasya vadha upaghātaḥ pīḍā pramā〈pa〉ṇaṃ vā hiṃsā nityatvena nātmochedaḥ | tatra yad uktaṃ tadabhāvaḥ sātmakapradāhe pi tannityatvād ity etan nopapadyate ||
