urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msP2D:3.1.14#tadātmaguṇasadbhāvād apratiṣedhaḥ | tasyā ātmaguṇatve sati sadbhāvād apratiṣedha ātmanaḥ yadi smṛtir ātmaguṇaḥ | evaṃ sati smṛtir upapadyate nānyadṛṣṭam anyaḥ smaratīti | iṃdriyacaitanye nānākartṛkāṇāṃ viṣayagrahaṇānām apratisaṃdhānaṃ pratisaṃdhāne vā viṣayavyavasthānupapatti ekas tu cetano ’nekārthadaśī bhinnanimittaḥ pūrvadṛṣṭam arthaṃ smaratīti ^" ekasyānekārthadarśino darśanapra[..]〈ti〉sandhānāt smṛter ātmaguṇatve sati sadbhāvaḥ viparyaye cānupapattiḥ smṛtyāśrayāḥ prāṇabhṛtāṃ sarve vyavahārāḥ ātmaliṃgam udāharaṇamātram iṃdriyāṃtaravikāra iti | aparisaṃkhyānāc ca smṛtiviṣayasya | apāresaṃkhyāya ca smṛtiviṣayam idam ucyate | na smṛteḥ smarttavyaviṣayatvād iti | yeyaṃ smṛtir agṛhyamāṇe ’rthe ajñāsiṣam aham amum artham iti etasyā jñātṛjñānaviśiṣṭaḥ pūrvajñāto rtho viṣayo nārthamātraṃ jñātavān aham amum arthaṃ asāv artho mayā jñātaḥ asminn arthe mama jñānam abhūd iti caturvidham etad vākyaṃ smṛtiviṣayajñāpakaṃ samānārthaṃ | sarva[kha]tra khalu jñātā jñānaṃ jñeyaṃ ca gṛhyate | atha pratyakṣe ’rthe yā smṛtis tayā trīṇi jñānāni ekasminn arthe pratisaṃdhīyaṃte samānakartṛkāṇi na nānākartṛkāṇi nākartṛkāṇi kiṃ tarhy ekakartṛkāṇi | adrākṣam amum arthai yam evaitarhi paśyāmi adrākṣam iti darśanaṃ da[rśe]〈rśa〉nasaṃvic ca ^" na khalv asaṃvidite sve darśane syād etad adrākṣam iti te khalv ete dve jñāne yam evaitarhi paśyāmīti tṛtīyaṃ jñānam evam eko rthas tribhir jñānair yujyamāno nākartṛko na nānākartṛkaḥ kiṃ tarhy ekakartṛka iti | so yaṃ smṛti〈viṣayo parisaṃkhyāyamāno vidyamānaḥ prajñāto rthaḥ pratiṣidhyate nāsty ātmā smṛteḥ smartavya[vi]〉viṣayatvād iti na cedaṃ smṛtimātraṃ smarttavyamātraviṣayaṃ idaṃ khalu jñānapratisaṃdhānavat smṛtipratisandhānam ekasya sarvaviṣayatvākta ^" eko yaṃ jñātā sarvaviṣayaḥ svāni jñānāni pratisaṃdhatte || amum arthaṃ jñāsyāmi amum arthaṃ vijānāmy amum arthaṃ ajñāsiṣam amum arthaṃ jijñāsamānaś ciram ajñātvādhyavasyaty ajñāsiṣam iti | evaṃ smṛtim api trikālaviśiṣṭāṃ susmūrṣāviśiṣṭāṃ ca pratisaṃdhatte | saṃskārasaṃtatimātre tu satve utpadyotpadya saṃskārās tirobhavati | sa nāsty eko pi saṃskāro yas trikālaviśiṣṭaṃ jñānaṃ smṛtiṃ cānubhave[kt]〈t〉 ^" na cā[nna]nubhava | m aṃtareṇa jñābhanasya smṛteś ca pratisaṃdhānam ahaṃ mameti cotpadyate dehāṃtaravakt ^" ato numīyate asty ekaḥ sarvaviṣamaḥ pratidehaṃ svajñānaprabaṃdhaṃ smṛtiprabaṃdhaṃ ca pratisaṃdhatta iti | yasya dehāṃtareṣu vṛtter abhāvān na pratisaṃdhānaṃ bhavatīti |
urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msP2D:3.1.15#nātmapratipattihetūnāṃ manasi saṃbhavākt ^"〈na dehādisaṃghātavyatirikta ātmā kasmāt ātmapratipattihetūnāṃ manasi saṃbhavāt〉 darśanasparśanābhyām ekārthagrahaṇād ity evamādīnām ātmapratipādakānāṃ hetūnāṃ manasi saṃbhavo yataḥ | mano hi sarvaviṣayam iti tasmān na śarīredriyamanobuddhisaṃghātavyatirikta ātmeti |
urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msP2D:3.1.16#jñātu(thā)r jñānasādhanopapatteḥ saṃjñāṃ bhedamātraṃ | jñātuḥ khalu jñānasādhanāny upapadyaṃte cakṣuṣā paśyati ghrāṇena jighrati sparśane ca spṛśati evaṃ maṃtuḥ sarvaviṣayasya matisādhanam aṃtaḥkaraṇabhūtaṃ sarvaviṣayaṃ vidyate yenāyaṃ manyeta prati | evaṃ sati jñātary ātmasaṃjñā na mṛṣyate manaḥsaṃjñābhyanujñāyate manasi ca manaḥsajñā na mṛṣyate matisādhanaṃ tv a[ḥ]bhyanujñāyate tad idaṃ sejñābhedamātra nārthe vivāda iti | pratyākhyāne vā sarvvedriyavilopaprasaṃgaḥ atha manmuḥ sarvaviṣayasya matisādhanaṃ sarvaviṣayaṃ pratyākhyāyate nāstīti | evaṃ rūpādiviṣayagrahaṇasādhanāny api asya na saṃti iti sarvedriyaviṣayalopaḥ prasajyata iti |
urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msP2D:3.1.17#niyamaś ca niranumānaḥ | yo yaṃ niyama iṣyate rūpādigrahaṇasādhanāny asya saṃti matisādhanaṃ sarvaviṣayaṃ nāstīti | ayaṃ niranumāno nātrānumānam asti yena niyamṛṃ pratipadyāṃmaha iti | rūpādibhyaś ca viṣayāṃtaraṃ sukhādayas tadupalabdhau karaṇāṃtarasadbhāvaḥ yathā cakṣuṣā gaṃdho na gṛhyata iti karaṇāṃtaraṃ ghrāṇam evaṃ cakṣurghrāṇābhyāṃ raso na gṛhyata iti karaṇāṃtaraṃ rasanaṃ ^" evaṃ śeṣeṣu ^" tathā cakṣurādibhiḥ sukhādayo na gṛhyaṃta iti karaṇāṃtareṇa bhavitavyaṃ | tac ca jñānāyaugapadyaliṃgaṃ | yac ca sukhādyupalabdhau karaṇaṃ tac ca jñānāyaugapadyaliṃgaṃ tasyeṃdriyam indriyaṃ prati sannidher asannidheḥ na yu[pa]〈ga〉pakt ^" jñānāny utpadyaṃte | tatra yad uktam ātmapratipattihetūnāṃ manasi saṃbhavād iti tad ayuktaṃ ^"
urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msP2D:3.1.18#kiṃ punar ayaṃ dehādisaṃghātād anyo nitya utānitya iti | kutaḥ saṃśayaḥ ubhayathā dṛṣṭatvāt saṃśayaḥ || vidyamānam ubhayathā bhavati nityam anityaṃ ca | pratipādite cātmasadbhāve saṃśayānivṛtter iti | ātmasadbhāvahetubhir evāsya prāg dehābhedād avasthānaṃ siddham ūrdhvam api dehabhedād avatiṣṭhate | kutaḥ || pūrvābhyastasmṛtyanubandhāj jātasya harṣabhayaśokasaṃpratipatteḥ || jātaḥ khalv ayaṃ kumārako asmiñ janmany agṛhīteṣu harṣabhayaśokahetuṣu harṣabhayaśokān pratipadyate liṅgānumeyān te ca smṛtyanubaṃdhād utpadyaṃta nānyathā | smṛtyannubaṃdhaś ca pūrvābhyāsam aṃtareṇa na bhavati | pūrvābhyāsaś ca pūrvajanmani sati nāṃnyatheti siddhyaty etad avatiṣṭhate ayam ūrddhvaṃ śarīrabhedād iti |
urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msP2D:3.1.19#padmādiṣu prabodhasaṃmīlanavikārava[ṃ] tadvikāraḥ yathā pa〈dmādiṣv anityeṣu pra[dho]bodhasammīlanaṃ vikāro bhavati evam ani[tyaṃs ta]〈tya〉syātmano harṣabhayaśokasaṃpratipa〉ttir vikāraḥ syā[kt]〈t〉 ^" hetvabhāvād ayukta | anena hetunā padmādiṣu prabodhasaṃmīlanavikāravad anityasyātmano harṣādisaṃpratipattir iti | nātrodāharaṇasādharmyāt sādhyasādhanaṃ hetur na vaidharmyād asti | hetvabhāvā[kt]〈t〉 asaṃbaddhārthakam apārthakam ucyata iti | dṛṣṭāṃtāc ca harṣādinimittasyānivṛttiḥ yā ceyam āseviteṣu viṣaye[śu]〈ṣu〉 harṣādisaṃpratipattiḥ smṛtyanubaṃdhakṛtā pratyātmaṃ gṛhyate seyaṃ padmādisaṃmīlanadṛ[ṣṭaṃ]〈ṣṭāṃ〉tena na nivarttyate | yathā ceyaṃ na nivarttaṃte tathā trātūsyāpīti kriyājātāś ca parṇavibhāgaḥ saṃyogaprabodhasaṃmīlane | kriyāhetuś ca kriyānumeya evaṃ ca sati kiṃ dṛṣṭāṃtena pratiṣidhyate |
urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msP2D:3.1.2#na viṣayavyavasthānākt ^" na dehādisaghātād anyaś cetanaḥ kasmād viṣayavyavasthānākt ^" vyavasthitaviṣayāṇīndriyāṇi cakṣuṣy asati rupaṃ na gṛhyate sati ca gṛhyate | yac caṃ yasminn asati na bhavati sati bhavati tasya tad iti vijñāyate | tasmād rūpagrahaṇaṃ cakṣuṣaḥ cakṣū [kta]〈rū〉rūpaṃ paśyati evaṃ ghrāṇādiṣv apīti | tānīdriyāṇī[ma]〈mā〉ni svasvaviṣayagrahaṇāc cetanāni iṃdriyāṇāṃ bhāvābhāvayor viṣayagrahaṇasya tathābhāvāktaḥ evaṃ sati kim anyena cetanena | saṃdigdhatvād ahetuḥ yo yam iṃdriyāṇāṃ bhāvābhāvayor viṣayagrahaṇasya tathābhāvaḥ sa kim ayaṃ cetanatvād āhosvic cetanopakaraṇānāṃ grahaṇanimitatvād iti saṃdihyate cetanopakaraṇatve pīṃdriyāṇāṃ graha[ṇā]〈ṇa〉nimittatvād bhavitum arhati |
urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msP2D:3.1.20#atha nirnimittaḥ padmādiṣu prabodhasaṃmīlanavikāra iti matam evam ātmano pi harṣādisaṃpratipattir iti | tac ca[ḥ] | noṣṇaśītavarṣakālanimittatvākt paṃcātmakavikārāṇāṃ | uṣṇādiṣu satsu bhāvād asatsv a[..]〈bhā〉vāt tannimittāḥ paṃcabhūtānugrahaṇa nirvṛttā[..]〈nā〉ṃ padmādīnāṃ prabodhasaṃmīlanavikārā iti | na nirnnimittāḥ evaṃ harṣādayo pi vikārā nimittād bhavitum arhaṃti na nimittam aṃtareṇa na cānyat pūrvābhyastasmṛtyanubaṃdhān nimittam astīti | na cotpattinirodhakāraṇānumānam ātmano dṛṣṭāṃtākt ^" na harṣādīnāṃ nimittam aṃtareṇotpattiḥ noṣṇādivan nimittāṃtaropādānaṃ harṣādīnāṃ tasmād ayuktaṃm etat |
urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msP2D:3.1.21#itaś ca nitya ātmā | pratyāhārābhyāsakṛtāt staṃnyābhilāṣākt jātamātrasya vatsasya pravṛttiliṃgaḥ stanyāṃbhilāṣo gṛhyate sa ca nāṃtareṇāhārābhyāsaṃ | kayā yuktyā | dṛśyate hi śarīriṇāṃ kṣudhā pīḍyamānānāṃ āhārābhyāsakṛtā[rt]〈t〉 smaraṇānubaṃdhād āhārābhilāṣaḥ | na ca pūrvaśarīram aṃtareṇāsau jātamātrasyopapadyate | tenānumīyate bhūta pūrvaṃ śarīraṃ yatrāṃnenāhāro bhyasta iti | sa khalv ayam ātmā pūrvaśarīrāt pretya śarīrāṃtaram āpannaḥ kṣutpīḍitaḥ pūrvābhyastam āhāram anusmaran stanyam abhilaṣati | tasmān na dehabhedād ātmā bhidyate bhavaty e[ddhva]vorddhvaṃ dehabhedād iti
urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msP2D:3.1.22#ayaso ’yaskāṃtābhigamanavat tadupasarpaṇaṃ || yathā khalv ayo bhyāsam aṃtareṇā’yaskāṃtam upasarpati evam āhārābhyāsam aṃtareṇa bā[lu]〈la〉 stanyam abhilaṣati |
urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msP2D:3.1.23#kim idam ayaso yaskāṃtābhisarpaṇaṃ nirnimittaṃ atha nimittād iti nirnimittaṃ tāvat nānyatra pravṛtyabhāvāt | yadi nirnimittaṃ lo〈hā〉dayo py ayaskāntam upasarpperyur ma jātu niyame kāraṇam astīti atha nimittāt tat kenopalabhyuta iti | kriyāliṃgaḥ kriyāhetuḥ kriyāniyamaliṃgaś ca kriyāhetuniyamaḥ tenānyatra pravṛttyabhāvaḥ bālasyāpi niyatam upasarthaṇakriyopalabhyate | na ca stanyābhilāṣaliṃgam anyadāhārābhyāsakṛtāt smaraṇānubaṃdhāt nimittaṃ dṛṣṭhāṃttenopapādyate | na cāsati nimitte kasyacid utpattiḥ na ca dṛṣṭāto dṛṣṭam abhilāṣahetuṃ bādhate | tasmād ayaso yaskāntābhigamanam adṛṣṭānta iti | ayasaḥ khalv api nānyatra pravṛttir bhavati | na jātv ayo loṣṭham upasarppati | kiṃkṛto sma niyama iti | yadi kāraṇaniyamāt sa ca kriyāniyamaligaḥ | evaṃ bālasyāpi niyataviṣayo bhilāṣaḥ kāraṇaniyamād bhavitum arhati | tac ca kāraṇam abhyastasmaraṇam anyad veti dṛṣṭena viśiṣyate dṛṣye hi śarīriṇām abhyastasmaraṇād āhārābhi[..]〈lā〉ṣa iti |
urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msP2D:3.1.24#itaś ca nitya ātmā | kasmāt | [dṛṣye hi śarīriṇām abhyastasmaraṇāhārābhilāṣa iti | itaś ca nitya ātmā | kasmāt] || vītarāgajanmādarśanāt | sarāgo jāyata ity arthād āpadyate | ayaṃ jāyamāno rāgānubaddho jāyate | rāgasya pūrvānubhūtaviṣayānuciṃtanaṃ yoniḥ pūrvānubhavaś ca viṣayāṇām anyasmin janmani śarīram aṃtareṇa nopapadyate so yam ātmā pūrvaśarīrānubhūvatān viṣayān anusmaran teṣu teṣu rajyate | tathā cāyaṃ dvayor janmanoḥ pratisaṃdhiḥ evaṃ pūrvaśarīrasya pūrvatareṇa pūrvatarasya pūrvatamenetyādinā’nādiś cetanasya śarīrayogaḥ anādiś ca rāgānubaṃdha iti siddhaṃ mityatvam iti |
urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msP2D:3.1.25#kathaṃ punar jñāyate pūr[va][〈vānubhūta〉]viṣayānuciṃtanajanito jātasya rāgo na punaḥ | saguṇadravyotpattivat tadutpattiḥ yathotpattidharmakasya dravyasya guṇāḥ kāraṇata utpadyaṃte tathotpattidharmakasyātmano rāgaḥ atrāyam uditānuvādo nidarśanārthaḥ |
urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msP2D:3.1.26#na saṃka[lpā]〈lpa〉nimittatvād rāgādīnāṃ | na khalu saguṇadravyotpattivad utpattir ātmano rāgasya ca kasmāt saṃkalpanimittatvād rāgādīnāṃ | ayaṃ khalu prāṇināṃ viṣayān āsevamānānāṃ saṃkalpajanito rāgo gṛhyate | saṃkalpaś ca pūrvānubhūtaviṣayānuciṃtanayoniḥ tenānumīyate jātasyāpi pūrvānubhūtārthaciṃtanakṛto rāga iti | ātmotpādādhikaraṇā tu rāgotpattir bhavaṃti saṃkalpād anyasmin rāgakāraṇe sati vācyā kāryadravyaguṇavat | na cātmotpādaḥ siddho nāpi saṃkalmād anyad rāgakāraṇam asti tasmād ayuktaṃ saguṇadravyotpattivat tayor utpattir iti | athāpi saṃkalmād anyad rāgakāraṇaṃ dharmādharmalakṣaṇam adṛṣṭam upādīyate tathāpi pūrvaśarīrayogo ’pratyākhyeyaḥ tatra hi tasyā nirvṛttiḥ nāsmin janmani tanmayatvād rāga iti | viṣayābhyāsaḥ khalv ayaṃ bhāvanāhetuḥ tanmayatvam ucyata iti || jātiviśeṣād rāgaviśeṣa iti karma khalv idaṃ jātiviśeṣanirvarttakaṃ | tādarthyā tāchabdaṃ vijñāyate tasmād anupapannaṃ saṃkalmād anyad rāgakāraṇam iti |
urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msP2D:3.1.27#anādiś cetanasya śarīrayoga ity uktaṃ svakṛtakarmanimittaṃ cāsya śarīraṃ sukhaduḥkhādhiṣṭhānaṃ tat parīkṣyate | kiṃ ghrānādivad ekaprakṛtikaṃ uta nānāprakṛtīti | kutaḥ saṃśayaḥ vipratipatteḥ saṃśayaḥ | pṛthivyādīni bhūtāni saṃkhyāvikalmena śarīraprakṛtir iti pratijānata iti | kiṃ tatra tattvaṃ | pārthivaṃ guṇāṃtaropalabdheḥ | tatra mānuṣaṃ śarīraṃ pārthivam kasmāt guṇāṃtaropalabdheḥ gaṃdhavatī pṛthivī gaṃdhavac ca śarīraṃ abādīnām agaṃdha[ṃ]tvāt | tatprakṛty agaṃdhaṃ syāt na tv idam abādibhir asaṃpṛktayā pṛthivyārabdhaṃ ceṣṭeṃdriyārthāśrayabhāvena kalpata ity ataḥ paṃcānāṃ bhūtānāṃ saṃyoge sati śarīraṃ bhavati bhūtasaṃyogo hi mithaḥ paṃcānāṃ na niṣiddhaḥ iti | āpyataijasavāyavyāni lokāṃtare śārīrāṇi tesv api bhūtasaṃyogaḥ puruṣārthataṃtra iti | sthālyādidravyaniḥpattāv api [niḥ pattāv api] niḥsaṃśaṃyā nābādisaṃyogam aṃtareṇṇa niṣpattir iti ||
urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msP2D:3.1.28_30#pārthivāpyataijasaṃ tadguṇopalabdheḥ | niḥśvāsocchvāsopalabdheś cāturbhautikaṃ | gaṃdhakledapākavyūhāvakāśadānebhyaḥ pāṃcabhautikaṃ | ta ime saṃdigdhāhetava ity upekṣitavān sūtrakāraḥ | kathaṃ saṃdigdhāḥ | sati ca prakṛtibhāve bhūtānāṃ dharmopalabdhir asa[ṃ]ti ca saṃyogāpratiṣedhāt | sannihitānām iti yathā sthālyām udakatejovāhyvākāśānām iti | tad idam anekabhūtaprakṛti śarīraṃm agaṃdham arasam arūpam asparśaṃ ca prakṛtyanuvidhānā[(ha)]t syāt | na tv idam itthaṃbhūtaṃ tasmāt pārthivaṃ guṇāṃtaropalabdheḥ |
urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msP2D:3.1.3#yac coktaṃ viṣayavyavasthānād iti || || tadvyavasthānād evātmasadbhāvād apratiṣedhaḥ | yadi khalv ekam iṃdriyam avyavasthitaviṣayaṃ sarvajñaṃ sarvaviṣayagrāhi cetanaṃ syākt kas tato nyacetanam anumātuṃ śaknuyā[kt]〈t〉 ^" yasmāt tu vyavasthitaviṣayāṇīṃdriyāṇi tasmāt tebhyo ’nyaś cetanaḥ sarvajñaḥ sarvaviṣayagrāhī viṣayavyavasthito numīyate ^" tatredam abhijjñānam apratyākhyeyaṃ cetanavṛttam udāhriyate | [kta]〈rū〉padarśī khalv ayaṃ ra[staṃ]〈saṃ〉 gaṃdhaṃ vā pūrvagṛhītam anuminoti gaṃdhaprativedī ca rūparasāv anuminoti | evaṃ viṣayaśeṣe pi vācyaṃ | rūpaṃ dṛṣṭvā gaṃdhaṃ jighrati ghrātvā ca gaṃdhaṃ rūpaṃ paśyati tad evam aniyataparyāyaṃ sarvaviṣayagrahaṇam ekacetanādhikaraṇam ananyakartṛkaṃ prati[staṃ]〈saṃ〉dhatte | pratyakṣānumānāgamasaṃśayapratyayāṃś ca nānāviṣayān svātmakartṛkān pratisaṃdhāya vedayate sarvaviṣayaṃ ca śāstraṃ pratipadyate | artham aviṣayabhūtaṃ śrotrasya kra[rp. (ma)‥ ‥ ‥ (ti)saṃdhāya vedayate (sarvaviṣayaṃ ca) śāstraṃ pratipadyate | artham aviṣayabhūtaṃ śrotrasya kra rp.]mabhāvino varṇān śrutvā padavākyabhārva pratisaṃdhāya śabdārthavyavasthāṃ ca budhyamāno ’nekaviṣayam arthajātam agrahaṇīyam akaikenedriyeṇa gṛhṇāti | seyaṃ sarvajñasya jñeyāvyavasthānupadaṃ na śakyā parikramituṃ ākṛtimātraṃ tūdāhṛtaṃ | tatra yad uktam idriyacaitanye sati kim anyena cetanena tad ayuktaṃ bhavati |
urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msP2D:3.1.31#śrutiprāmāṇyāc ca | sūryaṃ te cakṣur gachatād ity atra maṃtre pṛthivī te śarīram iti śrūyate | tad idaṃ prakṛtau vikārasya pralayābhidhānam iti | sūryaṃ te cakṣuḥ spṛṇomi ity atra maṃtrāṃtare pṛthivī te śarīraṃ spṛṇomī〈ti śrūyate〉 se〈yaṃ kā〉raṇād vikāra[syā]〈sya〉 spṛtir abhidhīyata iti | sthālyādiṣu ca tulyajātīyānām eka[kya]〈kā〉ryyāraṃbhadarśanāṃ[kt]〈t〉 bhinnajātīyānām ekakārmāraṃbhānupapattiḥ |
urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msP2D:3.1.32#athedānīm idriyāṇi prameyakrameṇa vicāryyaṃte | kim āvyaktikāny āhosvi[kt]〈t〉 bhautikānāti | kutaḥ saṃśayaḥ kṛṣṇasāre saty u[tpu]〈pa〉laṃbhād vyatiricya copalaṃbhāt saṃśayaḥ | kṛṣṇasāraṃ bhautikaṃ tasminn a〈nu〉pahate rūpopalaṃbdhiḥ upahate cānupalabdhir iti | vyatiricya kṛṣṇasāram a[ca]〈va〉sthitasya viṣayasya upalaṃbho na kṛṣṇasāraprāptasya na cāprāpakāritvam iṃdriyāṇāṃ | tad idam abhautikatve vibhutvāt saṃbhavati | evam ubhayadharmopalabdheḥ saṃśaya
urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msP2D:3.1.33#abhautikānīty āha | kasmāt | mahadaṇugrahaṇāt | mahad iti mahatta[raṃ]raṃ mahattamaṃ copalabhyate | yathā nyagrodhaparvatādi | aṇv iti aṇutaram aṇutamaṃ ca gṛhyate | nyagrodhadhānādi | tad ubhayam upalabhyamānaṃ cakṣuṣo bhautikatvaṃ bādhate | bhautikaṃ hi yāvat tāvad eva vyāpnoti | abhautikaṃ tu vibhutvāt sarvavyāpakam iti |
