urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msP2D:3.1.4#itaś ca dehādivyatirikta ātmā na dehādisaṅghātamātraṃ || śarīradāhe pātakābhāvāt | śarīragrahaṇena śarīredriyabuddhivedanāsaṃghātaḥ prāṇibhūto gṛhyate | prāṇibhūte śarīraṃ dahata prāṇihisāṃkṛtaṃ pāpaṃ [..]〈pā〉takam ity ucyate tasyābhāvaḥ tatphalena karttur asaṃbaṃdhā[kt]〈t〉 karttuś ca sabaṃdhāt śarīreṃdriyabuddhivedanāprabaṃdhe khalv anyaḥ saṃghā[kta]〈ta〉 utpadyate nyo nirudhyate | utpādanirodhasaṃtatibhūtaḥ prabaṃdho nānyatvaṃ bādhate | dehādisaṃghāta[ḥ] [tp prāṇibhūto hiṃsāṃ karoti nāsau hi tp]syānyatvādhiṣṭhānatvā[kt]〈t〉 ^" anyatvādhiṣṭhāno hy asau prakhyāyata iti | evaṃ ca sati yo dehādisaṃghātaḥ 〈tp prāṇibhūto hiṃsāṃ karoti nāsau hi tp〉sāphalena saṃbadhyate yaś ca saṃbadhyate [ne]〈na〉 tena hiṃsā kṛtā tad evaṃ satvabhede kṛtahāna[ha]m akṛtābhyāgamaḥ prasajyate | sati tu satvotpāde satva[rni]〈ni〉rodhe cākarmanimittaḥ satvasargaḥ prāpnoti | tatra muktyartho brahmacaryavāso na syā[kt]〈t〉 tad yadi dehādisaṃghātamātraṃ satvaṃ syā[kt]〈t〉 śarīradāhe pātakaṃ na bhave[kt]〈t〉 ^" aniṣṭaṃ caita[kt]〈t〉 tasmā dehādisaṃghātavyatirikta ātmā nitya iti |
urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msP2D:3.1.5#tadabhāvaḥ sātmakapradāhe pi tannityatvā[kt]〈t〉 || yasyāpi nityenātmanā sātmakaṃ śarīraṃ dahyate tasyāpi śarīradāhe pātakaṃ na bhaved dagdhuḥ | kasmān nityatvād ātmanaḥ na jātu kaścin nityaṃ hiṃsitum arhati | atha hiṃsyate nityatvam asya na bhavati | seyam ekasmin pakṣe hiṃsa niḥphalāny asmiṃ[(kh)a]s tv anupapanneti |
urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msP2D:3.1.6#na kāryāśrayakartṛvadhā[kt]〈t〉 ^" na kramo nityasya satvasya vadho hiṃsā | api tv anuchitidharmakasya satvasya kāryāśrayasya śarīrasya svaviṣayopalabdheś ca kartṝṇām iṃdriyāṇām upaghātaḥ pīḍā vaikalyalakṣaṇaḥ | prabaṃdhochedo 〈vā〉 pramāpaṇalakṣaṇo vā vadho hiṃseti | kāryaṃ tu sukhaduḥkhasaṃvedanaṃ tasyāyatanam adhiṣṭhānam āśrayaḥ śarīraṃ | kāryāśrayasya śarīrasya svaviṣayopalabdheś ca kartṝṇām idriyāṇāṃ vadho hiṃsā na nityasyātmanaḥ | tatra [(d)u]〈yad u〉ktaṃ tadabhāvaḥ sātmakapradāhe pi [tā]〈ta〉[vi]〈nni〉tyatvād ity etad ayuktaṃ yasya satvochedo hiṃsā tasya kṛtahānam akṛtābhyāgamaś ceti doṣaḥ | etāvac caitat syā[kt]〈t〉 ^" satvochedo vā hiṃsā | nuchittidharmakasya satvasya kāryāśrayakartṛvadho vā na kalpāṃtaram asti satvochedaś ca pratiṣiddhaḥ | tatra kim anya cheṣaṃ yathābhūtam iti | athavā kāryāśrayakartṛvadhād iti | kāryāśrayo dehe | driyakaddhisaṃghāto nityasyā[ṃ]tmanaḥ tatra sukhaduḥkhapratisaṃvedanaṃ tasyādhiṣṭhānam āśrayaḥ tadāyatanaṃ tad bhavati na tato nyad iti sa eva ka[ṃ]rttā tannimittā hi sukhaduḥkhasaṃvedanasya nirvṛttiḥ na tadaṃtareṇeti tasya vadha upaghātaḥ pīḍā pramāpaṇaṃ vā hiṃsā na nityatvenātmochedaḥ | tatra yad uktaṃ tadabhāvaḥ sātmakapradāhe pi tatmityatvād etan neti |
urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msP2D:3.1.7#itaś ca dehādivyatirikta ātmā | savyadṛṣṭasyetareṇa pratyabhijñānāt | pūrvāparayor vijñānayor ekaviṣaye pratisaṃdhitānaṃ pratyabhijñānaṃ | tam evaitarhi paśyāmi yam ajñāsiṣaṃ sa evāyam artha iti | savyena cakṣuṣā dṛṣṭam athetareṇāpi cakṣuṣā pratyabhijñānā[kt]〈t〉 | yam adrākṣaṃ tam evaitarhi paśyāmīti | iṃdriyacaitanye tu nānyadṛṣṭam anyaḥ pratyabhijānātīti pratyabhijñānānupapattiḥ | asti v idaṃ pratyabhijñānaṃ tasmād iṃdriyavyatiriktaś cetanaḥ |
