urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msS1S:3.1.16#jñātur iti || jñātur jñānasādhanopapatteḥ saṃjñābhedamātram || jñātuḥ khalu jñānasādhanāny utpadyante cakṣuṣā paśyati ghrāṇena jighrati sparśanena spṛśati evaṃ mantuḥ sarvaviṣayasya matisādhanam antaḥkaraṇabhūtaṃ sarvaviṣayaṃ vidyate yenāyaṃ manyata iti evaṃ ca sati jñātary ātmasaṃjñā na mṛṣyate manaḥsaṃjñā [mṛ] bhyate matisādhanam abhyanujñāyate tad idaṃ saṃjñābhedamātraṃ nārthe vivāda iti 19 pratyākhyāne veti || pratyākhyāne vā sarvendriyavilopaprasaṅgaḥ || atha mantuḥ sarvaviṣayasya pratisādhanaṃ sarvaviṣayaṃ pratyākhyāyate nāstīti evaṃ rūpādiviṣayagrahaṇasādhanāny api na bhavantīti sarvendriyalopaḥ prasajyata iti 20
urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msS1S:3.1.17#niyama iti || niyamas tu niranumānaḥ || yo yaṃ niyama iṣyate rūpādigrahaṇasādhanāny asya santi matisādhane tu sarvaviṣayaṃ nāstīti ayaṃ ca niyamo niranumāno nātrānumātrānumānam asti yena niyamaṃ pratipadyāmaha iti rūpādibhyaś ca viṣayāntaraṃ sukhādayas tadupalabdhau kāraṇāntarasambhavaḥ yathā cakṣuṣā gandho na gṛhyate iti karaṇāntaraṃ ghrāṇam eva cakṣurghrāṇābhyāṃ raso na gṛhyata iti karaṇāntaraṃ rasanam evaṃ śeṣeṣv api tathā cakṣurādibhiḥ sukhādayo na gṛhyanta iti karaṇāntareṇa bhavitavyaṃ tac ca jñānāyaugapadyaliṅgaṃ yac ca sukhādilabdhau karaṇaṃ tac ca jñānāyaugapadyaliṅgam tasyendriyam indriyaṃ prati sannidher asannidheś ca na yugapaj jñānāni jāyanta iti tatra yad uktaṃ ātmapratipattihetūnāṃ manasi sambhavād iti tad ayuktam
urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msS1S:3.1.18#kim punar ayaṃ dehādisaṅghātād anyo nitya utānitya iti kutaḥ saṃśayaḥ ubhayathā dṛṣṭatvāt saṃśayaḥ vidyamānam ubhayathā bhavati nityam anityaṃ ca pratipādite cārthasadbhāve saṃśayānivṛtter iti ātmasadbhāvahetubhir evāsya prāg dehabhedād avasthānaṃ siddham ūrdhvam api dehabhedād avatiṣṭhante 20 kutaḥ pūrveti || pūrvābhyastasmṛtyanubandhāj jātasya harṣabhayaśokasampratipatteḥ || jātaḥ khalv ayaṃ kumārako smiñ janmany agṛhīteṣu harṣabhayaśokahetuṣu harṣabhayaśokān sampratipadyate liṅgānumeyān te ca smṛtyanubandhād utpadyante nānyathā smṛtyanubandhaś ca pūrvābhyatsam antareṇa na bhavati pū rvābhyāsaś ca pūrvajanmani sati nānyathā sidhyati tasmād avatiṣṭhate yam ūrdhvaṃ śarīrabhedād iti 22
urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msS1S:3.1.19#padmādiṣv iti || padmādiṣu prabodhasammīlanavikāravat tadvikāraḥ || yathā padmādiṣv anityeṣu prabodhaḥ sammīlanaṃ ca vikāro bhavati evam anityasyātmano harṣabhayaśokasampratipattiś ca syāt 23 hetvabhāvād iti || hetvabhāvād ayuktam || anyena hetunā padmādiṣu prabodhanaṃ sammīlanaṃ vikāravad anityasyātmano harṣādisampratipattir iti nātrodāharaṇasādharmyāt sādhyasādhanaṃ hetur na vaidharmyād asti hetvabhāvād asambaddhārtham apārthakam ucyeta iti 24 dṛṣṭāntāc ceti || dṛṣṭāntāc ca harṣādinimittasyānivṛttiḥ || yā ceyam āseviteṣu viṣayeṣu harṣādisampratipattiḥ smṛtyanubandhakṛtā pratyātmaṃ gṛhyate sā ceyaṃ padmādiprabodhasammīladṛṣṭāntena na nivarteta yathā ceyaṃ na nivartyeta tathā jātasyāpi kriyājāś ca padmasaṃyogavibhāgāḥ padmaprabodhasammīlane kriyāhetuś ca kriyānumeyaḥ evam ca kiṃ dṛṣṭāntena pratiṣidhyate 25
urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msS1S:3.1.2#viṣayavyavasthānāt || na dehādisaṅghātād anyaś cetanaḥ kasmād viṣayavyavasthānāt vyavasthitaviṣayāṇīndriyāṇi cakṣuṣy asati rūpaṃ na gṛhyate sati ca gṛhyate yac ca tasminn asati na bhavati sati ca bhavatīti tasya tad iti vijñāyeta tasmād rūpagrahaṇaṃ cakṣuṣaś cakṣū rūpaṃ paśyati evaṃ ghrāṇādiṣv apīti 3 tānīndriyāṇi svasvaviṣayagrahaṇāc cetanāni ^" tathā cendriyāṇā〈nīmā〉m iti 4 indriyāṇāṃ bhāvābhāvayor viṣayagrahaṇasya tathābhāvāt 4 || evaṃ sati kim anyena cetanena sandigdhatvād iti ^"^" sandigdhatvād ahetuḥ ^"^" yo yam indriyāṇāṃ bhāvābhāvayor viṣayagrahaṇasya tathābhāvaḥ sa kim ayaṃ cetanatvāc cetanopakaraṇānāṃ vā grahaṇanimittatvād iti sandihate cetanopakaraṇatve pīndriyāṇāṃ grahaṇanimittatvād bhavitum arhati 5 ^"^"
