urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msS1S:3.1.26#neti na saṅkalpanimittatvād rāgādīnām na khalu guṇadravyotpattivat tadutpattir ātmano rāgasya ca kasmāt saṅkalpanimittatvād rāgādīnām ayaṃ khalu prāṇināṃ viṣayāṇām sevyamānānāṃ saṅkalpajanito rāgo gṛhyate saṅkalpaḥ pūrvānubhūtaviṣayānucintanayoniḥ tenānumīyate jātasyāpi pūrvānubhūtānumitta na kṛto rāga iti ^" ātmotpādādhikaraṇāt tu rāgotpattir bhavantī saṅkalpād anyasmin rāgakāraṇe sati vācyā kāryadravyaguṇavat na cātmotpādaḥ siddho nāpi saṅkalpād anyad rāgakāraṇam asti tasmād ayuktaṃ saguṇadravyotpattivat tayor utpattiḥ athāpi saṅkalpād anyad rāgakāraṇaṃ dharmādharmalakṣaṇame dṛṣṭam upādadīta ^" tathāpi pūrvaśarīrayogo pratyākhyeyaḥ tatra hi tasya nivṛttir nānyasmiñ janmani 34 tanmayatvād iti ^" tanmayatvād rāgaḥ 35 ^"^" viṣayābhyāsaḥ khalv ayaṃ bhāvanāhetuḥ tanmayatvam ucyata iti 35 ^"^" jātīti jātiviśeṣāc ca rāgavi〈śeṣaḥ 36 ||〉 karma khalv idaṃ jātiviśeṣanimittaṃ tādarthyāt tacchabdaṃ vijñāyate tasmād anupapannaṃ saṅkalpād anyad rāgakāraṇam iti
