urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msU1D:3.1.15#nātmapratipattihetūnāṃ manasi saṃbhavā〈t〉 na saṃghātavyatirikta ātmā kasmāt ātmapratipattihetūnāṃ manasi saṃbhavāt || darśanasparśanābhyām ekārthagrahaṇād ity evamādīnām ātmapratipādakānāṃ manasi saṃbhavān mano hi sarbabiṣayam iti tasmān na śarīreṃdriyamanovyatirikta ātmā ||
urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msU1D:3.1.16#jñātur jñānasādhanopapatteḥ saṃjñābhedamātraṃ || jñātuḥ khalu jñānasādhanāny upapadyaṃte || cakṣuṣā paśyati ghrāṇena jighrati sparśanena spṛśati || evaṃ maṃtuḥ sarbaviṣayamatisādhanaṃm anaḥkaraṇa〈bhūtaṃ sarba〉viṣayaṃ vidyate yenāyaṃ manyata iti || evaṃ sati jñātaryy ātmasaṃjñā na mṛṣyate manaḥsaṃjñā pyanujñāyate || manasi ca manaḥsaṃjñā 〈na〉 mṛṣyate || matisādhanasaṃjñā mṛṣyate mati sā dhanem abhyanujñāyate || tad idaṃ saṃjñābhedamātraṃ nātmani vivāda iti || pratyākhyāne bā sarbeṃdriya-bilopaprasaṅgaḥ 〈||〉 atha maṃtuḥ sarbaviṣayasya matisādha〈naṃ〉 sarbabiṣayaṃ pratyākhyāyate nāstīti || evaṃ rūpādibiṣayagrahaṇasādhanāny api na bhavaṃti iti sarbeṃdriyabiṣayalopa〈na〉ṃ prasajyata iti ||
urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msU1D:3.1.17#niyamaś ca niranumānaḥ || yo yaṃ niyama iṣyate rūpādigrahaṇasādhanāny asya saṃti | matisādhanaṃ sarbabiṣayaṃ nāstīti ayaṃ 〈niyamo〉 niranumāno 〈’〉tra nānumānam asti yena niyamaṃ pratipadyāmaha iti rūpādibhyaś ca biṣayāṃtaraṃ sukhādayas tadupalabdhau karaṇāṃtarasadbhāvaḥ yathā cakṣuṣā gaṃdho na gṛhyate iti karaṇāṃtaraṃ ghrāṇam evaṃ cakṣurghrāṇābhyāṃ raso na gṛhyate iti karaṇāṃtaraṃ rasanaṃ || evaṃ śeṣeṣv api || tathā cakṣu[ṣ]〈r〉ādibhiḥ sukhādayo na gṛhyaṃte iti karaṇāṃtareṇa bhavitavyaṃ tac ca jñānāyaugapadyaṃ liṃgam yac ca sukhādyupalabdhau karaṇaṃ tac ca jñānāyaugapadyaliṃgaṃ tasyeṃdriyam iṃdriyaṃ prati saṃnidher asaṃnidher na yugapat jñānāny utpadyaṃta iti || tatra yad uktam ātmapratipattihetūnāṃ manasi saṃbhavād iti tad ayuktaṃ 〈||〉
urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msU1D:3.1.18#kiṃ punar ayaṃ dehādisaṃghātād anyo nitya utānitya iti || kutaḥ saṃśayaḥ ^" ubhayathā dṛṣṭatvāt saṃśayaḥ ^" bidyamānam ubhayathā bhavati || nityam anityaṃ ca pratipādite cātmasaṃbhave saṃśayānibṛtter iti || ātmasadbhāvahetubhir evāsya prāg dehabhedād ava-sthānaṃ siddhaṃ || ūrddhvam api dehabhedād avatiṣṭhate || kutaḥ || pūrbābhyastasmṛtyanubaṃdhāj jātasya harṣabhayaśokasaṃpratipatteḥ || jātaḥ khalv ayaṃ kumārako asmin janmani agṛhīteṣu [he]〈ha〉rṣabhayaśokahetuṣu harṣabhayaśokān pratipadyate liṃgānumeyāt || te ca smṛtyanubaṃdhād utpadyante nānyathā || smṛtyanubaṃdhaś ca pūrbābhyāsam antareṇa na bhavati || pūrbābhyāsaś ca pūrbajanmani sati nānyatheti sidhyatīty etad avatiṣṭhate ayam ūrddhvaṃ śarīrabhedād iti ||
urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msU1D:3.1.19#padmādiṣu prabodhasaṃmīlanabikāravat tadbikāraḥ || yarthānityeṣu padmādiṣu prabodha〈ḥ〉 saṃmīlanaṃ bikāro bhavati || evam anityātmano harṣabhayaśokasaṃpratipattiḥ syāt || hetvabhāvād ayuktaṃ anena hetunā padmādiṣu pravodhasaṃmīlanabikārabad anityasyātmano harṣādisaṃpratipattir iti ||nātrodāharaṇasādharmyāt sādhyasādhanaṃ hetur na vaidharmyād asti hetvabhāvā[da]〈t〉 || [‥]〈a〉saṃbaddhārthakam apārthakam ucyata iti || dṛṣṭāṃtāc ca harṣādinimittasyānibṛttiḥ | yā ceyam āseviteṣu biṣayeṣu harṣādisaṃpratipattiḥ smṛtyanubaṃdhakṛtā pratyātmaṃ gṛhyate seyaṃ padmādisammīlanadṛṣṭāntena na nivarttyate || yathā ceyaṃ na nibarttyate tathā jātasyāpīti kriyājātāś ca parṇasaṃyogabibhāgāḥ prabodhasammīlane kriyāhetuś ca kriyānumeyaḥ || evaṃ ca kiṃ dṛṣṭāntena pratiṣidhyate ||
urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msU1D:3.1.2#na biṣayavyavasthānāt || na dehādisaṃghātād anyaś cetanaḥ kasmāt biṣayavyavasthānāt | vyavasthitabiṣayāṇīṃdriyāṇi || cakṣuṣy asati rūpaṃ na gṛhyate || sati ca gṛhyate || yac ca yasminn asati na bhavati sati bhavati tasya tad iti bijñāyate tasmād rūpaṃ grahaṇaṃ cakṣuṣaḥ cakṣū rūpaṃ paśyati evaṃ ghrāṇāṃ [jighratīti] tānīṃdriyā-ṇīmāni svasvabiṣayagrahaṇāc cetanāni iṃdriyāṇāṃ bhāvābhāvayor biṣayagrahaṇasya tathābhāvāt | evaṃ sati kim anyena 〈cetanena〉2 saṃdigdhatvād ahetuḥ || yo yam iṃdriyāṇāṃ bhāvābhāvayor biṣayagrahaṇasya tathābhāvaḥ sa kim ayaṃ cetanatvād āhosvic cetanopakaraṇa〈nāṃ〉2 grahaṇanimittatvād iti saṃdihyate cetanopakaraṇatve pīṃdriyāṇāṃ grahaṇanimittatvād bhavitum arhati ||
urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msU1D:3.1.20#atha nirnimittaḥ padmādiprabodhasammīlanavikāra iti || matam evam ātmano harṣādisaṃpratipattir iti tac ca na || uṣṇaśītabarṣākālanimittatvāt paṃcātmakavikārāṇām || uṣṇādiṣu satsu bhāvād asatsv abhāvāt tannimittāḥ paṃcabhūtānugraheṇa nirbṛttānāṃ padmādīnāṃ prabodhasamīlanabikārā iti na nirnimittā evaṃ harṣādayo pi bikārā nimittād bhavitum arhaṃtīti || na nimitta[ṃ]m antareṇa || na bā’nyat pūrbābhyastasmṛtyanubaṃdhān nimittam astīti || na cotpattinirodhakāraṇānumānam ātmano dṛṣṭāntāt na harṣādīnāṃ nimittam antareṇotpattiḥ noṣṇādivan nimittāntaropādānaṃ tasmād ayuktam etat ||
urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msU1D:3.1.21#itaś ca nitya ātmā || pretyāhārābhyāsakṛtāt stanyābhilāṣāt || jātamātrasya batsasya pravṛttiliṃgaḥ stanyābhilāṣo gṛhyate || sa ca nāṃtareṇāhārābhyāsaṃ ^" kayā yuktyā dṛśyate hi śarīriṇāṃ kṣudhā pīḍyamānānā[ṃ]mr āhārābhyāsakṛtāt smaraṇānubaṃdhād āhārābhilāṣaḥ || na tu pūrvaśarīrābhyāsam antareṇāsau jātamātrasyopapadyate || tenānumīyate bhūtapūrbaṃ śarīraṃ yatrānenāhāro bhyasta iti || sa khalv ayam ātmā pūrbaśarīrāt pretya śarīrāṃtaram āpannaḥ kṣutpīḍitaḥ pūrbābhyastam āhāram anusmaran stanyam abhilaṣati || tasmān na dehabhedād ātmā bhidyate bhavaty evorddhvaṃ dehabhedād iti ||
