urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msU1D:3.1.23#kim idam ayaso yaskāntābhigamanaṃ nirnimitta[‥]〈m a〉tha nimittād iti nirnimittaṃ tāvat || nānyatra pra(bṛ)‥ ‥ ‥ ‥ yadi nirnimittaṃ loṣṭādayo pi ayaskāṃtam upasarppeyur na jātu niyame kāraṇam astīti || atha nimittāt tat kenopalabhyata iti || kriyāliṃgaḥ kriyāhetuḥ kriyāniyamaliṃgaś ca kriyāniyamahetuniyamaḥ tenānyatra prabṛttyabhāvaḥ bālasyāpi niyatam upasarpaṇakriyopalabhyate na ca stanyābhilāṣaliṃgam anyadāhārābhyāsakṛtāt smaraṇānubaṃdhāt nimittaṃ dṛṣṭāṃtenopapādyate || na cāsati nimitte kasyacid utpattiḥ na ca dṛṣṭāṃto dṛṣṭam abhilāṣahetuṃ bādhate || tasmād aya〈so〉 yaskāṃtābhigamanam adṛṣṭāṃta iti || ayasaḥ khalv api nānyatra prabṛttir bhavati || na jātv ayo loṣṭam upasarppati || kiṃkṛto sya niyama iti || yadi kāraṇaniyamaḥ sarbakriyāniyamaliṃgaḥ evaṃ bālasyāpi niyatabiṣayo bhilāṣaḥ kāraṇaniyamād bhavitum arhati || tac ca kāraṇam abhyastasmaraṇam anyad beti dṛṣṭena biśiṣyate || dṛṣṭo hi śarīriṇām abhyastasmaraṇād āhārābhilāṣa iti
urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msU1D:3.1.24#itaś ca nitya ātmā kasmāt || vītarāgajanmādarśanāt || sarāgo jāyata ity arthād āpadyate | [ayaṃ jāyamāna ity arthād āpadyate] ayaṃ jāyamāno rāgānubaddho jāyate || rāgasya pūrvānubhūtaviṣayānuciṃtanaṃ yoniḥ pūrbānubhavaś ca biṣayāṇām pūrbasmin janmani śarīram antareṇa no〈pa〉padyate so yam ātmā pūrbaśarīrānubhūtān biṣayān anusmarans teṣu teṣu rajyate tathā cāyaṃ dvayoḥ 〈janmanoḥ〉2 pratisaṃdhiḥ evaṃ pūrbaśarīrasya pūrbatareṇa pūrba〈tara〉śarīrasya pūrbatamenetyādinā’nādiś cetanasya śarīrayogaḥ anādiś ca rāgānubaṃdha iti siddhaṃ nityatvam iti ||
