urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msU1D:3.1.26#na saṃkalpanimittatvād rāgādīnām || na khalu saguṇadravyotpattivat tad utpattir ātmano rāgasya ca ^" kasmāt saṃkalpanimittatvād rāgādīnām || ayaṃ khalu prāṇināṃ biṣayān āsevamānānāṃ saṃkalpajanito rāgo gṛhyate || saṃkalpaś ca pūrbānubhūtabiṣayānuciṃtanayoniḥ tenānumīyate jātasyāpi pūrbānubhūtārthaciṃtanakṛto rāga iti || ātmo[ātmotpādo adhikaraṇaṃ sādhyaṃ yai sveṣāṃ tair bācyety arthaḥ]tpādādhikaraṇānāṃ tu rāgotpattir bhavatīti saṃkalpād anyasmin rāgakāraṇe sati bācyā kāryadravyaguṇavat || na cātmotpādaḥ siddho nāpi saṃkalpād anyad rāgakāraṇam asti || tasmād ayuktaṃ saguṇadravyotpattivat tayor utpattiḥ || athāpi saṃkalpād anyad rāgakāraṇaṃ dharmādharmalakṣaṇam adṛṣṭam upādīyate || tathāpi pūrbaśarīrayogo ’pratyākhyeyaḥ tatra hi tasya nirvṛttiḥ nāsmin janmani ^" tanmayatvād rāga iti biṣayābhyāsaḥ khalv ayaṃ bhāvanāhetuḥ tanmayatvam ucyata iti || jātiviśeṣāc ca rāgabiśeṣa iti || karma khalv idaṃ jātibiśeṣanirbarttakaṃ tādātmyāt tācchabdyaṃ bijñāyate tasmād tad anupapannaṃ saṃkalpād anyad rāgakāraṇam iti ||
