urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msV2D:3.1.2#na viṣayavya(vasthānā)t ^" na dehādisaṃghātād anyaś cetanaḥ kasmād viṣayavyavasthānāt ^" vyavasthitaviṣayāṇīṃdriyāṇi cakṣuṣy asati rūpaṃ na gṛhyate sati ca gṛhyate yac ca tasminn asati na bhavati sati ca bhavati tasya tad iti vijñāyate tasmād rūpagrahaṇaṃ cakṣuṣaḥ cakṣū rūpaṃ paśyati evaṃ ghrāṇādiṣv apīti | tānīmānīṃdriyāṇi svasvaviṣayagrahaṇāc cetanāni iṃdriyāṇāṃ bhāvābhāvayor viṣayagrahaṇa[syā]〈sya〉 tathābhāvāt ^" evaṃ sati kim anyena cetanena | saṃdigdhatvād ahetuḥ yo yam iṃdriyāṇāṃ bhāvābhāvayor viṣayagrahaṇasya tathābhāvaḥ sa kim ayaṃ cetanatvād āhosvic cetanopakaraṇānāṃ grahaṇanimitatvād iti saṃdihyate cetanopakaraṇatve pīṃdriyāṇāṃ grahaṇanimittatvād bhavitum arhati |
