urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msV7D:3.1.17#niyamaś ca niranumānaḥ || so yaṃ niyama iṣyate rūpādigrahaṇasādhanāny asya santi matisādhanaṃ tu sarvaviṣaṃ nāstīti | ayaṃ niyamo niranumāno nātrānumānam asti yena niyamaṃ pratipattyāmaha iti rūpādibhyaś ca viṣayāntaraṃ sukhādayaḥ tadupalabdhau karaṇāntarasaṃbhavaḥ | yathā cakṣuṣā na gaṃdho gṛhyate iti karaṇāntaraṃ ghrāṇam evaṃ cakṣughrāṇābhyāṃ raso na gṛhyata iti karaṇāntaraṃ rasanaṃ evaṃ śeṣeṣv api tathā cakṣurādibhiḥ sukhādayo na gṛhyanta iti karaṇāntareṇa bhavitavyaṃ tac ca jñānāyaupadyaliṃgaṃ yac ca sukhādyupala(bdh)au karaṇaṃ tac ca jñānāyaugapadyaliṃgaṃ tasyeṃdriyam iṃdriyaṃ prati sannidher asannidheś ca na yugapaj jñānāni jāṃyanta iti tatra yad uktam ātmapratipattihetūnāṃ manasi saṃbhavād iti tad ayuktaṃ |
