urn:cts:sktlit:skt0001.nyaya002.msV7D:3.1.2#na viṣayavyavasthānāt || na dehādisaṃghātād anyaś cetanaḥ kasmāt viṣayavyavasthānāt vyavasthitaviṣayāṇīṃdriyāṇi cakṣuṣy asati rūpaṃ na gṛhyate sati ca gṛhyate tac ca tasminn asati na bhavati sati ca bhavati tasya tad iti vijñāyate tasmād rūpagrahaṇaṃ cakṣuḥ cakṣū rūpaṃ paśyati evaṃ ghraṇādiṣv apīti tānīmānīṃdriyāṇi svasvaviṣayagrahaṇāc cetanān iṃdriyāṇāṃ bhāvābhāvayor viṣayagrahaṇasya tathābhāvāt | evaṃ sati kim anyena cetanena saṃdigdhatvād ahetuḥ yo yam idriyāṇāṃ bhāvābhāvayor viṣayagrahaṇasya tathābhāvaḥ sa kim ayaṃ cetanatvāc cetanopakaraṇānāṃ vā grahaṇanimittatvād iti saṃdihyate cetanopakaraṇatve pīṃdriyāṇāṃ grahaṇanimittatvād bhavitum arhati ||
